256void ResetFuelConversions()
257{
258 long i;
259
260 for (i = 0;
261 i < 257;
262 i++) // could also read default file here
263 fuelconversion.Type[i] = i;
264 fuelconversion.Type[0] = -1;
265 for (i = 91; i < 100; i++)
266 fuelconversion.Type[i] -= 100;
267 HAVE_CONV_MODELS = false;
268}

279 FuelMod.ModelIsHere[Changes]=false;

282 HAVE_CUST_MODELS=false;

286void mainCmd(int argc, char* argv[])
287{
288 char ProjectFile[256] = "";
289 bool FilesOK = true;
290 char ErrMsg[256] = "";
291
292 if (argc == 2)
293 {
294 FILE* testfile;
295
296 strcpy(ProjectFile, argv[1]);
297 if ((testfile = fopen(ProjectFile, "r")) == NULL)
298 {
299 sprintf(ErrMsg, "%s %s", ProjectFile, "Could Not Be Opened");
300 FilesOK = false;
301 }
302 fclose(testfile);
303 }
304 if (!FilesOK)
305 {
306 printf("ERROR:%s\n\n", ErrMsg); exit(1);
307 }
308}
309
313bool ReadIgnitions(char* igfi)
314{
315 double PI = 3.1415926536;
316 long NumIgnitions;
317 char IgnitionFile[256] = ""; //"ignition.txt";
318 char points[256], lines[256], polys[256], TestEnd[20],
319 NewIgnitionFile[256];
320 long count, count1, count2, startsize = 5;
321 long fposition1, OldNumIgnitions = 0;
322 double CenterX, CenterY, xpt, ypt, angle;//, FireArea;
323 FILE* ignitions;
324 FILE* ignitionfile;
325 headdata NewHeader; // header information structure
326 bool IgnitionFileExists = false;
327 memset(points, 0x0, sizeof points);
328 memset(lines, 0x0, sizeof lines);
329 memset(polys, 0x0, sizeof polys);
330 memset(TestEnd, 0x0, sizeof TestEnd);
331
332 if ((ignitions = fopen(IgnitionFile, "r")) == NULL)
333 {
334 // ErrorNumber=9;
335 return false;
336 }
337
338 while (!feof(ignitions))
339 {
340 fscanf(ignitions, "%s", NewIgnitionFile);
341 if (feof(ignitions))
342 break;
343 OldNumIgnitions++;
344
345 if (OldNumIgnitions <= NumIgnitions)
346 continue;
347
348 if ((ignitionfile = fopen(NewIgnitionFile, "r")) == NULL)
349 continue;
350
351 NumIgnitions = OldNumIgnitions;
352 fscanf(ignitionfile, "%s", points);
353 if (feof(ignitionfile))
354 {
355 fclose(ignitionfile);
356 continue;
357 }
358 fscanf(ignitionfile, "%s %s", lines, polys);
359 fclose(ignitionfile);
360 if ((ignitionfile = fopen(points, "r")) != NULL)
361 {
362 fscanf(ignitionfile, "%s", TestEnd);
363 if (feof(ignitionfile))
364 {
365 fclose(ignitionfile);
366 ignitionfile = 0;
367 }
368 else if (ignitionfile)
369 {
370 while (!feof(ignitionfile))
371 {
372 if (strcmp(TestEnd, "END"))
373 {
374 fscanf(ignitionfile, "%lf %lf", &CenterX, &CenterY);
375 CenterX -= ((long) (NewHeader.WestUtm / 1000)) * 1000;
376 CenterY -= ((long) (NewHeader.SouthUtm / 1000)) * 1000;
377 AllocPerimeter1(GetNewFires(), 11); // 10 points, 11th is for bounding box
378 for (count = 0; count <= 9; count++)
379 {
380 angle = (double (count) * (PI / 5.0));
381 xpt = CenterX + (cos(angle) * startsize);
382 ypt = CenterY + (sin(angle) * startsize);
383 SetPerimeter1(GetNewFires(), count, xpt, ypt);
384 SetFireChx(GetNewFires(), count, 0, 0);
385 }
386 SetNumPoints(GetNewFires(), count);
387 SetInout(GetNewFires(), 1);
388 IncNewFires(1);
389 BoundingBox();
390 fscanf(ignitionfile, "%s", TestEnd);
391 }
392 else
393 {
394 fclose(ignitionfile);
395 IgnitionFileExists = true;
396 break;
397 }
398 }
399 }
400 }
401
402 if ((ignitionfile = fopen(lines, "r")) != NULL)
403 {
404 fscanf(ignitionfile, "%s", TestEnd);
405 if (feof(ignitionfile))
406 {
407 fclose(ignitionfile);
408 ignitionfile = 0;
409 }
410 else if (ignitionfile)
411 {
412 while (strcmp(TestEnd, "END"))
413 {
414 fposition1 = ftell(ignitionfile);
415 count = 0;
416 do
417 {
418 fscanf(ignitionfile, "%s", TestEnd);
419 if (!strcmp(TestEnd, "END"))
420 break;
421 fscanf(ignitionfile, "%lf", &CenterY);
422 count++;
423 }
424 while (strcmp(TestEnd, "END"));
425 fseek(ignitionfile, fposition1, SEEK_SET);
426 if (count == 2)
427 {
428 AllocPerimeter1(GetNewFires(), 5); // 1 more for bounding box
429 fscanf(ignitionfile, "%lf %lf", &CenterX, &CenterY);
430 fscanf(ignitionfile, "%lf %lf", &xpt, &ypt);
431 CenterX -= ((long) (NewHeader.WestUtm / 1000)) * 1000;
432 CenterY -= ((long) (NewHeader.SouthUtm / 1000)) * 1000;
433 xpt -= ((long) (NewHeader.WestUtm / 1000)) * 1000;
434 ypt -= ((long) (NewHeader.SouthUtm / 1000)) * 1000;
435 SetPerimeter1(GetNewFires(), 0, CenterX, CenterY);
436 SetFireChx(GetNewFires(), 0, -1.0, 0.0); // 100% of equilibrium spread
437 SetPerimeter1(GetNewFires(), 2, xpt, ypt);
438 SetFireChx(GetNewFires(), 2, -1.0, 0.0); // 100% of equilibrium spread
439 double xdiff, ydiff, midx, midy;//, oppslope;
440 xdiff = CenterX - xpt;
441 ydiff = CenterY - ypt;
442 midx = CenterX - xdiff / 2.0; //-xdiff/100.0;
443 midy = CenterY - ydiff / 2.0; //-xdiff/100.0*oppslope;
444 SetPerimeter1(GetNewFires(), 1, midx, midy);
445 SetFireChx(GetNewFires(), 1, -1.0, 0.0); // 100% of equilibrium spread
446 SetPerimeter1(GetNewFires(), 3, midx, midy);
447 SetFireChx(GetNewFires(), 3, -1.0, 0.0); // 100% of equilibrium spread
448 count = 3;
449 }
450 else
451 {
452 AllocPerimeter1(GetNewFires(), 2 * count - 1); // 1 more for bounding box
453 //count1=0;
454 count2 = 2 * count - 3;
455 for (count1 = 0; count1 < count; count1++)
456 {
457 fscanf(ignitionfile, "%lf %lf", &CenterX, &CenterY);
458 CenterX -= ((long) (NewHeader.WestUtm / 1000)) * 1000;
459 CenterY -= ((long) (NewHeader.SouthUtm / 1000)) * 1000;
460 SetPerimeter1(GetNewFires(), count1, CenterX,
461 CenterY);
462 SetFireChx(GetNewFires(), count1, -1.0, 0.0); // 100% of equilibrium spread
463 if (count1 > 0 && count1 < count - 1) // write points bacward in array
464 {
465 SetPerimeter1(GetNewFires(), count2, CenterX,
466 CenterY);
467 SetFireChx(GetNewFires(), count2, -1.0, 0.0); // 100% of equilibrium spread
468 --count2;
469 }
470 }
471 }
472 fscanf(ignitionfile, "%s", TestEnd);
473 SetNumPoints(GetNewFires(), 2 * count - 2);
474 SetInout(GetNewFires(), 1);
475 IncNewFires(1);
476 BoundingBox(); // find bounding box for line source
477 fscanf(ignitionfile, "%s", TestEnd);
478 }
479 fclose(ignitionfile);
480 IgnitionFileExists = true;
481 }
482 }
483
484 if ((ignitionfile = fopen(polys, "r")) != NULL)
485 {
486 fscanf(ignitionfile, "%s", TestEnd);
487 if (feof(ignitionfile))
488 {
489 fclose(ignitionfile);
490 ignitionfile = 0;
491 //break;
492 }
493 else if (ignitionfile)
494 {
495 while (strcmp(TestEnd, "END"))
496 {
497 fposition1 = ftell(ignitionfile);
498 count = 0;
499 do
500 {
501 fscanf(ignitionfile, "%s", TestEnd);
502 if (!strcmp(TestEnd, "END"))
503 break;
504 fscanf(ignitionfile, "%lf", &CenterY);
505 count++;
506 }
507 while (strcmp(TestEnd, "END"));
508 fseek(ignitionfile, fposition1, SEEK_SET);
509 count1 = count;
510 AllocPerimeter1(GetNewFires(), count1 + 1); // 1 more for bounding box
511 for (count = 0; count < count1; count++)
512 {
513 fscanf(ignitionfile, "%lf %lf", &CenterX, &CenterY);
514 CenterX -= ((long) (NewHeader.WestUtm / 1000)) * 1000;
515 CenterY -= ((long) (NewHeader.SouthUtm / 1000)) * 1000;
516 SetPerimeter1(GetNewFires(), count, CenterX, CenterY);
517 SetFireChx(GetNewFires(), count, -1.0, 0.0); // 100% of equilibrium spread
518 }
519 fscanf(ignitionfile, "%s", TestEnd);
520 SetNumPoints(GetNewFires(), count1);
521 SetInout(GetNewFires(), 1);
522 IncNewFires(1);
523 if (arp() < 0)
524 ReversePoints(1);
525 BoundingBox(); // find bounding box for line source
526 fscanf(ignitionfile, "%s", TestEnd);
527 }
528 fclose(ignitionfile);
529 IgnitionFileExists = true;
530 }
531 }
532 }
533 fclose(ignitions);
534
535 return IgnitionFileExists;
536}

629void BoundingBox()
630{
631 /*
632 double xpt, ypt, Xlo, Xhi, Ylo, Yhi;
633 long NumFire=GetNewFires()-1;
634 long NumPoint=GetNumPoints(NumFire);
635
636 Xlo=Xhi=GetPerimeter1Value(NumFire, 0, 0);
637 Ylo=Yhi=GetPerimeter1Value(NumFire, 0, 1);
638 for(int i=1; i<NumPoint; i++)
639 { xpt=GetPerimeter1Value(NumFire, i, 0);
640 ypt=GetPerimeter1Value(NumFire, i, 1);
641 if(xpt<Xlo) Xlo=xpt;
642 else
643 { if(xpt>Xhi)
644 Xhi=xpt;
645 }
646 if(ypt<Ylo) Ylo=ypt;
647 else
648 { if(ypt>Yhi)
649 Yhi=ypt;
650 }
651 }
652 SetPerimeter1(NumFire, NumPoint, Xlo, Xhi);
653 SetFireChx(NumFire, NumPoint, Ylo, Yhi);
654 */
655}

775
776void SetLandscapeViewPort(double north, double south, double east, double west)
777{
778 double cols, rows, f, ic, ir;
779
780 ViewPortNorth = north;
781 ViewPortSouth = south;
782 ViewPortEast = east;
783 ViewPortWest = west;
784 rows = ((ViewPortNorth - ViewPortSouth) / GetCellResolutionY());
785 f = modf(rows, &ir);
786 NumViewNorth = (long) ir;
787 if (f > 0.50)
788 NumViewNorth++;
789 cols = ((ViewPortEast - ViewPortWest) / GetCellResolutionX());
790 f = modf(cols, &ic);
791 NumViewEast = (long) ic;
792 if (f > 0.5)
793 NumViewEast++;
794}
795
796void GetLandscapeViewPort(double* north, double* south, double* east,
797 double* west)
798{
799 *north = ViewPortNorth;
800 *south = ViewPortSouth;
801 *east = ViewPortEast;
802 *west = ViewPortWest;
803}

1209
1210
1211FuelConversions::FuelConversions()
1212{
1213 long i;
1214
1215 for (i = 0;
1216 i < 257;
1217 i++) // could also read default file here
1218 Type[i] = i;
1219 Type[99] = -1;
1220 Type[98] = -2;
1221 Type[97] = -3;
1222 Type[96] = -4;
1223 Type[95] = -5;
1224 Type[94] = -6;
1225 Type[93] = -7;
1226 Type[92] = -8;
1227 Type[91] = -9;
1228}
1229
1230
1231int GetFuelConversion(int fuel)
1232{
1233 // retrieve fuel model conversions
1234 int cnv = -1;
1235
1236 if (fuel >= 0 && fuel < 257) // check fuel for valid array range
1237 {
1238 cnv = fuelconversion.Type[fuel]; // get new fuel
1239 if (cnv < 1) // if not
1240 {
1241 if (cnv < -9)
1242 cnv = -1;
1243 //if(cnv!=0 && cnv!=-1 && cnv!=-2)
1244 // cnv=-1; // return rock of other than -1 or -2
1245 }
1246 else if (!IsNewFuelReserved(cnv)) //NewFuel>13 && NewFuel<51) // check to see if custom model required
1247 {
1248 if (newfuels[cnv].number == 0) // check to see if cust mod here
1249 cnv = -1; // return rock if no fuel model
1250 }
1251 else if (cnv > 256) // if new fuel too high
1252 cnv = -1;
1253 }
1254
1255 return cnv;
1256}
1257
1258
1259int SetFuelConversion(int From, int To)
1260{
1261 // set fuel model conversions
1262 if (From >= 0 && From < 257 && To < 257 && To >= 0)
1263 {
1264 if (To > 90 && To < 100)
1265 To = To - 100; // make all negative for the 90's, indicate unburnable
1266 else if (To == 0)
1267 To = -1;
1268 fuelconversion.Type[From] = To;
1269 }
1270 else
1271 return false;
1272
1273 return true;
1274}

1611
1612void SetVectorFileName(const char* FileName)
1613{
1614 memset(VectFName, 0x0, sizeof(VectFName));
1615 sprintf(VectFName, "%s", FileName);
1616 FILE* newfile;
1617

1635void SetRasterFileName(const char* FileName)
1636{
1637 memset(RasterArrivalTime, 0x0, sizeof(RasterArrivalTime));
1638 memset(RasterFireIntensity, 0x0, sizeof(RasterFireIntensity));
1639 memset(RasterFlameLength, 0x0, sizeof(RasterFlameLength));
1640 memset(RasterSpreadRate, 0x0, sizeof(RasterSpreadRate));
1641 memset(RasterHeatPerArea, 0x0, sizeof(RasterHeatPerArea));
1642 memset(RasterCrownFire, 0x0, sizeof(RasterCrownFire));
1643 memset(RasterFireDirection, 0x0, sizeof(RasterFireDirection));
1644 memset(RasterReactionIntensity, 0x0, sizeof(RasterReactionIntensity));
1645 memset(RastFName, 0x0, sizeof(RastFName));
1646 sprintf(RasterArrivalTime, "%s%s", FileName, ".toa");
1647 sprintf(RasterFireIntensity, "%s%s", FileName, ".fli");
1648 sprintf(RasterFlameLength, "%s%s", FileName, ".fml");
1649 sprintf(RasterSpreadRate, "%s%s", FileName, ".ros");
1650 sprintf(RasterHeatPerArea, "%s%s", FileName, ".hpa");
1651 sprintf(RasterCrownFire, "%s%s", FileName, ".cfr");
1652 sprintf(RasterFireDirection, "%s%s", FileName, ".sdr");
1653 sprintf(RasterReactionIntensity, "%s%s", FileName, ".rci");
1654 sprintf(RastFName, "%s%s", FileName, ".rst");
1655}

1657
1658char* GetRasterFileName(long Type)
1659{
1660 if (Type == 0)
1661 return RastFName;
1662 if (Type == RAST_ARRIVALTIME)
1663 return RasterArrivalTime;
1664 if (Type == RAST_FIREINTENSITY)
1665 return RasterFireIntensity;
1666 if (Type == RAST_FLAMELENGTH)
1667 return RasterFlameLength;
1668 if (Type == RAST_SPREADRATE)
1669 return RasterSpreadRate;
1670 if (Type == RAST_HEATPERAREA)
1671 return RasterHeatPerArea;
1672 if (Type == RAST_CROWNFIRE)
1673 return RasterCrownFire;
1674 if (Type == RAST_FIREDIRECTION)
1675 return RasterFireDirection;
1676 if (Type == RAST_REACTIONINTENSITY)
1677 return RasterReactionIntensity;
1678
1679 return NULL;
1680}

1857bool CreateRasterOverlay(char *FileName, double *max, double *min)

1874 rMinVal=1e300;

1876 if(!strcmp(TestRead, "north:")) // GRASS File

1878 fscanf(Rast, "%s", TestRead);
1879 fscanf(Rast, "%lf", &rS);

1886 fscanf(Rast, "%s", TestRead);
1887 fscanf(Rast, "%ld", &rCols);
1888 rCellSizeY=(rN-rS)/(double) rRows;
1889 rCellSizeX=(rE-rW)/(double) rCols;
1890 }
1891 else if(!strcmp(strupr(TestRead), "NCOLS")) // ARC grid file
1892 { fscanf(Rast, "%ld", &rCols);
1893 fscanf(Rast, "%s", TestRead);
1894 fscanf(Rast, "%ld", &rRows);
1895 fscanf(Rast, "%s", TestRead);
1896 fscanf(Rast, "%lf", &rW);
1897 fscanf(Rast, "%s", TestRead);
1898 fscanf(Rast, "%lf", &rS);
1899 fscanf(Rast, "%s", TestRead);
1900 fscanf(Rast, "%lf", &rCellSizeX);
1901 fscanf(Rast, "%s", TestRead);
1902 fscanf(Rast, "%s", TestRead);
1903 rN=rS+rCellSizeX*(double) rRows;
1904 rE=rW+rCellSizeX*(double) rCols;
1905 rCellSizeY=rCellSizeX;
1906 }

1913 { fscanf(Rast, "%lf", &value);
1914 RasterOverlay[i*rCols+j]=value;
1915 if(value>=0.0)
1916 { if(value<rMinVal)
1917 rMinVal=value;
1918 if(value>rMaxVal)
1919 rMaxVal=value;
1920 }
1921 }
1922 }
1923 fclose(Rast);
1924
1925 *max=rMaxVal;
1926 *min=rMinVal;
1927
1928 rW=ConvertUtmToEastingOffset(rW);
1929 rE=ConvertUtmToEastingOffset(rE);
1930 rN=ConvertUtmToNorthingOffset(rN);

1932

1934}

1943
1944double QueryRasterOverlay(double xcoord, double ycoord)
1945{
1946 if(RasterOverlay==0)
1947 return -2;
1948 if(xcoord<rW || xcoord>rE)
1949 return -3;
1950 if(ycoord<rS || ycoord>rN)
1951 return -4;
1952
1953 double xpt, ypt;
1954 long easti, northi, posit;
1955
1956 xpt=(xcoord-rW)/rCellSizeX;
1957 ypt=(ycoord-rS)/rCellSizeY;
1958 easti=((long) xpt);
1959 northi=((long) ypt);
1960 northi=rRows-northi-1;
1961 if(northi<0)
1962 northi=0;
1963 posit=(northi*rCols+easti);
1964
1965 return RasterOverlay[posit];
1966}

1970{
1971 if(RasterOverlay)
1972 return true;
1973
1974 return false;
1975}

2060
2061long GetVisPerimFile(long* xpt, long* ypt)
2062{
2063 if (VP)
2064 {
2065 if (fscanf(VP, "%ld %ld", xpt, ypt) == EOF) // end of file
2066 return -1;
2067 else
2068 {
2069 if (*xpt < 0)
2070 return 0; // end of fire polygon
2071 else
2072 return 1; // successful read
2073 }
2074 }
2075
2076 return -1;
2077}

2080void SetVisPerimFile(long xpt, long ypt)
2081{
2082 if (!VP)
2083 return;
2084
2085 MemPerim[MemCount * 2] = xpt;
2086 MemPerim[MemCount * 2 + 1] = ypt;
2087 MemCount++;
2088 if (MemCount > MaxCount - 1)
2089 {
2090 for (i = 0; i < MemCount; i++)
2091 fprintf(VP, "%ld %ld\n", MemPerim[i * 2], MemPerim[i * 2 + 1]);
2092 MemCount = 0;
2093 }
2094 //if(VP)
2095 // fprintf(VP, "%ld %ld\n", xpt, ypt);
2096}

2098
2099void SetVisPerimPoint(long xpt, long ypt, long firenum)
2100{
2101 // Writes "point" to file nad ends fire
2102 if (!VP)
2103 return;
2104
2105 if (MemCount < MaxCount - 2)
2106 {
2107 MemPerim[MemCount * 2] = xpt;
2108 MemPerim[MemCount * 2 + 1] = ypt;
2109 MemCount++;
2110 MemPerim[MemCount * 2] = xpt + 1;
2111 MemPerim[MemCount * 2 + 1] = ypt + 1;
2112 MemCount++;
2113 MemPerim[MemCount * 2] = -firenum;
2114 MemPerim[MemCount * 2 + 1] = -1;
2115 MemCount++;
2116 }
2117 else
2118 {
2119 for (i = 0; i < MemCount; i++)
2120 fprintf(VP, "%ld %ld\n", MemPerim[i * 2], MemPerim[i * 2 + 1]);
2121 MemCount = 0;
2122 fprintf(VP, "%ld %ld\n", xpt, ypt);
2123 fprintf(VP, "%ld %ld\n", xpt + 1, ypt + 1);
2124 fprintf(VP, "%ld %ld\n", -firenum, -1L);
2125 }
2126}

2129long OpenVisPerimFile(int readfromstart)
2130{
2131 long FilePos = 0;
2132
2133 //WaitForSingleObject(hVisperimSemaphore, INFINITE);
2134 if (readfromstart)
2135 {
2136 if ((VP = fopen(VisPerim, "r")) != NULL)
2137 fseek(VP, 0, SEEK_SET);
2138 }
2139 else
2140 {
2141 if ((VP = fopen(VisPerim, "r")) != NULL)
2142 {
2143 fseek(VP, 0, SEEK_END);
2144 FilePos = ftell(VP);//fgetpos(VP, &FilePos);
2145 fclose(VP);
2146 }
2147 VP = fopen(VisPerim, "a");
2148 if (VP == NULL)
2149 {
2150 //SetFileAttributes(VisPerim, FILE_ATTRIBUTE_NORMAL);
2151 chmod(VisPerim,S_IRWXO);
2152 VP = fopen(VisPerim, "a");
2153 }
2154 }
2155
2156 return FilePos;
2157}

2280//------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2281//------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2282//
2283// Attached Vectors
2284//
2285//------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2286//------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2287
2288VectorStorage* CurVect = 0;
2289VectorStorage* FirstVect = 0;
2290VectorStorage* NextVect = 0;
2291VectorStorage* LastVect = 0;
2292
2293void SetNumVectorThemes(long number)
2294{
2295 NumVectorThemes = number;
2296}
2297
2298
2299long GetNumVectorThemes()
2300{
2301 return NumVectorThemes;
2302}
2303
2304
2305long AllocVectorTheme()
2306{
2307 if (FirstVect == 0)
2308 {
2309 if ((FirstVect = new VectorStorage[1]) == NULL)
2310 return -1;
2311// ZeroMemory(FirstVect, sizeof(VectorStorage));
2312 memset(FirstVect,0x0, sizeof(VectorStorage));
2313 CurVect = FirstVect;
2314 CurVect->last = 0;
2315 CurVect->next = 0;
2316 }
2317 else
2318 {
2319 long i;
2320
2321 CurVect = FirstVect;
2322 for (i = 0; i < NumVectorThemes; i++)
2323 {
2324 LastVect = CurVect;
2325 NextVect = (VectorStorage *) CurVect->next;
2326 CurVect = NextVect;
2327 }
2328 if ((CurVect = new VectorStorage[1]) == NULL)
2329 return -1;
2330// ZeroMemory(CurVect, sizeof(VectorStorage));
2331 memset(CurVect,0x0, sizeof(VectorStorage));
2332 CurVect->last = (VectorStorage *) LastVect;
2333 if (LastVect)
2334 LastVect->next = (VectorStorage *) CurVect;
2335 CurVect->next = 0;
2336 }
2337 NumVectorThemes++;
2338
2339 return NumVectorThemes - 1;
2340}
2341
2342
2343bool SetVectorOnOff(long FileNum, long OnOff)
2344{
2345 long i;
2346
2347 CurVect = FirstVect;
2348 for (i = 0; i < NumVectorThemes; i++)
2349 {
2350 NextVect = (VectorStorage *) CurVect->next;
2351 if (i == FileNum)
2352 break;
2353 CurVect = NextVect;
2354 }
2355 if (OnOff >= 0)
2356 CurVect->theme.OnOff = (bool) OnOff;
2357
2358 return CurVect->theme.OnOff;
2359}

2362VectorTheme* GetVectorTheme(long FileNum)

2364 long i;
2365
2366 CurVect = FirstVect;
2367 for (i = 0; i < NumVectorThemes; i++)
2368 {
2369 NextVect = (VectorStorage *) CurVect->next;
2370 if (i == FileNum)
2371 break;
2372 CurVect = NextVect;

2390 }
2391 // memcpy(&CurVect->theme, Theme, sizeof(VectorTheme));
2392 memcpy(&CurVect->theme, Theme, sizeof(VectorTheme));
2393}
2394
2395
2396VectorTheme* SetNewVectorTheme(VectorTheme* Theme)
2397{
2398 long i;
2399
2400 LastVect = 0;
2401 CurVect = FirstVect;
2402 for (i = 0; i < NumVectorThemes; i++)
2403 {
2404 LastVect = CurVect;
2405 NextVect = (VectorStorage *) CurVect->next;
2406 CurVect = NextVect;
2407 }
2408 if ((CurVect = new VectorStorage[1]) == NULL)
2409 return NULL;
2410// ZeroMemory(CurVect, sizeof(VectorStorage));
2411 memset(CurVect,0x0, sizeof(VectorStorage));
2412 CurVect->last = (VectorStorage *) LastVect;
2413 if (LastVect)
2414 LastVect->next = (VectorStorage *) CurVect;
2415 CurVect->next = 0;
2416 memcpy(&CurVect->theme, Theme, sizeof(VectorTheme));
2417 if (FirstVect == 0)
2418 FirstVect = CurVect;
2419 NumVectorThemes++;
2420
2421 return &CurVect->theme;
2422}
2423
2424
2425void FreeVectorTheme(long FileNum)
2426{
2427 long i;
2428 VectorStorage* TempVect;
2429
2430 CurVect = FirstVect;
2431 for (i = 0; i < NumVectorThemes; i++)
2432 {
2433 NextVect = (VectorStorage *) CurVect->next;
2434 if (i == FileNum)
2435 break;
2436 CurVect = NextVect;
2437 }
2438 TempVect = CurVect;
2439 LastVect = (VectorStorage *) TempVect->last;
2440 CurVect = (VectorStorage *) TempVect->next;
2441 if (CurVect)
2442 CurVect->last = (VectorStorage *) LastVect;
2443 delete[]TempVect;
2444 if (FileNum == 0)
2445 FirstVect = CurVect;
2446 else if (LastVect)
2447 LastVect->next = (VectorStorage *) CurVect;
2448 NumVectorThemes--;
2449}
2450
2451
2452void FreeAllVectorThemes()
2453{
2454 CurVect = FirstVect;
2455 for (i = 0; i < NumVectorThemes; i++)
2456 {
2457 NextVect = (VectorStorage *) CurVect->next;
2458 if (CurVect)
2459 delete[] CurVect;
2460 CurVect = NextVect;
2461 }
2462 if (CurVect)
2463 delete[] CurVect;
2464 FirstVect = 0;
2465 CurVect = 0;
2466 NextVect = 0;
2467 NumVectorThemes = 0;
2468}
2469
2470//--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2471//
2472// manage weather/wind stream data
2473//
2474//--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2475
2476bool CalcFirstLastStreamData()
2477{
2478 bool BadRange = false;
2479 long sn;
2480 unsigned long FirstWtr, FirstWnd, LastWtr, LastWnd;
2481 double ipart, fract;
2482
2483 for (sn = 0; sn < GetNumStations(); sn++)
2484 {
2485 if (AtmosphereGridExists() < 2)
2486 {
2487 if (!wtrdt[sn] || (!wddt[sn] && AtmosphereGridExists() == 0))
2488 {
2489 continue;
2490 }
2491 }
2492
2493 FirstWtr = (unsigned long)((GetJulianDays(FirstMonth[sn].wtr) + FirstDay[sn].wtr) * 1440.0);
2494 fract = modf((double) FirstHour[sn].wnd / 100.0, &ipart);
2495 FirstWnd = (unsigned long)((GetJulianDays(FirstMonth[sn].wnd) + FirstDay[sn].wnd) * 1440.0 +
2496 ipart * 60.0 +
2497 fract);
2498 LastWtr = (unsigned long)((GetJulianDays(LastMonth[sn].wtr) + LastDay[sn].wtr) * 1440.0);
2499 fract = modf((double) LastHour[sn].wnd / 100.0, &ipart);
2500 LastWnd = (unsigned long)((GetJulianDays(LastMonth[sn].wnd) + LastDay[sn].wnd) * 1440.0 +
2501 ipart * 60.0 +
2502 fract);
2503
2504 if (FirstWtr > LastWtr)
2505 LastWtr += (unsigned long)(365.0 * 1440.0);
2506 if (FirstWnd > LastWnd)
2507 LastWnd += (unsigned long)(365.0 * 1440.0);
2508
2509 if (FirstWnd <= FirstWtr)
2510 {
2511 if (LastWnd <= FirstWtr)
2512 BadRange = true;
2513 }
2514 else if (FirstWnd > FirstWtr)
2515 {
2516 if (FirstWnd > LastWtr)
2517 BadRange = true;
2518 }
2519 if (BadRange)
2520 {
2521 FirstMonth[sn].all = 0;
2522 FirstDay[sn].all = 0;
2523 FirstHour[sn].all = 0;
2524
2525 return false;
2526 }
2527
2528 if (FirstMonth[sn].wtr > FirstMonth[sn].wnd)
2529 {
2530 FirstMonth[sn].all = FirstMonth[sn].wtr;
2531 FirstDay[sn].all = FirstDay[sn].wtr;
2532 FirstHour[sn].all = FirstHour[sn].wtr;
2533 }
2534 else if (FirstMonth[sn].wtr < FirstMonth[sn].wnd)
2535 {
2536 FirstMonth[sn].all = FirstMonth[sn].wnd;
2537 FirstDay[sn].all = FirstDay[sn].wnd;
2538 FirstHour[sn].all = FirstHour[sn].wnd;
2539 }
2540 else
2541 {
2542 FirstMonth[sn].all = FirstMonth[sn].wtr;
2543 if (FirstDay[sn].wtr > FirstDay[sn].wnd)
2544 {
2545 FirstDay[sn].all = FirstDay[sn].wtr;
2546 FirstHour[sn].all = FirstHour[sn].wtr;
2547 }
2548 else if (FirstDay[sn].wtr < FirstDay[sn].wnd)
2549 {
2550 FirstDay[sn].all = FirstDay[sn].wnd;
2551 FirstHour[sn].all = FirstHour[sn].wnd;
2552 }
2553 else
2554 {
2555 FirstDay[sn].all = FirstDay[sn].wnd;
2556 if (FirstHour[sn].wtr > FirstHour[sn].wnd)
2557 FirstHour[sn].all = FirstHour[sn].wtr;
2558 else
2559 FirstHour[sn].all = FirstHour[sn].wnd;
2560 }
2561 }
2562 if (LastMonth[sn].wtr < LastMonth[sn].wnd)
2563 {
2564 LastMonth[sn].all = LastMonth[sn].wtr;
2565 LastDay[sn].all = LastDay[sn].wtr;
2566 LastHour[sn].all = LastHour[sn].wtr;
2567 }
2568 else if (LastMonth[sn].wtr > LastMonth[sn].wnd)
2569 {
2570 LastMonth[sn].all = LastMonth[sn].wnd;
2571 LastDay[sn].all = LastDay[sn].wnd;
2572 LastHour[sn].all = LastHour[sn].wnd;
2573 }
2574 else
2575 {
2576 LastMonth[sn].all = LastMonth[sn].wtr;
2577 if (LastDay[sn].wtr < LastDay[sn].wnd)
2578 {
2579 LastDay[sn].all = LastDay[sn].wtr;
2580 LastHour[sn].all = LastHour[sn].wtr;
2581 }
2582 else if (LastDay[sn].wtr > LastDay[sn].wnd)
2583 {
2584 LastDay[sn].all = LastDay[sn].wnd;
2585 LastHour[sn].all = LastHour[sn].wnd;
2586 }
2587 else
2588 {
2589 LastDay[sn].all = LastDay[sn].wnd;
2590 if (LastHour[sn].wtr < LastHour[sn].wnd)
2591 LastHour[sn].all = LastHour[sn].wtr;
2592 else
2593 LastHour[sn].all = LastHour[sn].wnd;
2594 }
2595 }
2596 }
2597
2598 return true;
2599}

2603//--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2604//
2605// Manage Atmosphere Grid with regular Weather/Wind Stream Data
2606//
2607//--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2608
2609
2610void SetCorrectStreamNumbers()
2611{
2612 long i;
2613
2614 if (AtmosphereGridExists() == 1) // if wind grid only
2615 {
2616 for (i = 0; i < 5; i++)
2617 FreeWindData(i);
2618 if (NumWeatherStations > 0)
2619 NumWindStations = NumWeatherStations;
2620 else
2621 NumWindStations = 1;
2622 for (i = 0; i < NumWindStations; i++)
2623 {
2624 FirstMonth[i].wnd = AtmGrid->GetAtmMonth(0);
2625 LastMonth[i].wnd = AtmGrid->GetAtmMonth(AtmGrid->GetTimeIntervals() -
2626 1);
2627 FirstDay[i].wnd = AtmGrid->GetAtmDay(0);
2628 LastDay[i].wnd = AtmGrid->GetAtmDay(AtmGrid->GetTimeIntervals() -
2629 1);
2630 FirstHour[i].wnd = AtmGrid->GetAtmHour(0);
2631 LastHour[i].wnd = AtmGrid->GetAtmHour(AtmGrid->GetTimeIntervals() -
2632 1);
2633 }
2634 }
2635 else if (AtmosphereGridExists() == 2) // if weather and wind grids
2636 {
2637 for (i = 0; i < 5; i++)
2638 {
2639 FreeWindData(i);
2640 FreeWeatherData(i);
2641 }
2642 i = 0;
2643 NumWindStations = 1;
2644 NumWeatherStations = 1;
2645 FirstMonth[i].wnd = AtmGrid->GetAtmMonth(0);
2646 LastMonth[i].wnd = AtmGrid->GetAtmMonth(AtmGrid->GetTimeIntervals() -
2647 1);
2648 FirstDay[i].wnd = AtmGrid->GetAtmDay(0);
2649 LastDay[i].wnd = AtmGrid->GetAtmDay(AtmGrid->GetTimeIntervals() - 1);
2650 FirstHour[i].wnd = AtmGrid->GetAtmHour(0);
2651 LastHour[i].wnd = AtmGrid->GetAtmHour(AtmGrid->GetTimeIntervals() - 1);
2652 FirstMonth[i].wtr = AtmGrid->GetAtmMonth(0);
2653 LastMonth[i].wtr = AtmGrid->GetAtmMonth(AtmGrid->GetTimeIntervals() -
2654 1);
2655 FirstDay[i].wtr = AtmGrid->GetAtmDay(0);
2656 LastDay[i].wtr = AtmGrid->GetAtmDay(AtmGrid->GetTimeIntervals() - 1);
2657 FirstHour[i].wtr = AtmGrid->GetAtmHour(0);
2658 LastHour[i].wtr = AtmGrid->GetAtmHour(AtmGrid->GetTimeIntervals() - 1);
2659 }
2660}

2683
2684long AllocWindData(long StatNum, long NumObs)
2685{
2686 long StationNumber = StatNum;
2687
2688 if (wddt[StationNumber])
2689 {
2690 delete[] wddt[StationNumber];
2691 wddt[StationNumber] = 0;
2692 MaxWindObs[StatNum] = 0;
2693 }
2694 else
2695 {
2696 StationNumber = GetOpenWindStation();
2697 if (StationNumber < 5)
2698 NumWindStations = StationNumber + 1;
2699 }
2700 if (StationNumber<5 && NumObs>0)
2701 {
2702 size_t nmemb = MaxWindObs[StationNumber] = NumObs*2; // alloc 2* number needed
2703 if ((wddt[StationNumber] = new WindData[nmemb]) == NULL)
2704 StationNumber = -1;
2705 }
2706 else
2707 StationNumber = -1;
2708
2709 return StationNumber;
2710}
2711
2712
2713void FreeWindData(long StationNumber)
2714{
2715 if (wddt[StationNumber])
2716 {
2717 delete[] wddt[StationNumber];//free(wddt[StationNumber]);
2718 NumWindStations--;
2719 MaxWindObs[StationNumber] = 0;
2720 }
2721 wddt[StationNumber] = 0;
2722 FirstMonth[StationNumber].wnd = 0;
2723 LastMonth[StationNumber].wnd = 0;
2724 FirstDay[StationNumber].wnd = 0;
2725 LastDay[StationNumber].wnd = 0;
2726 FirstHour[StationNumber].wnd = 0;
2727 LastHour[StationNumber].wnd = 0;
2728}

2731long SetWindData(long StationNumber, long NumObs, long month, long day,
2732 long hour, double windspd, long winddir, long cloudy)
2733{
2734 if (NumObs < MaxWindObs[StationNumber])
2735 {
2736 wddt[StationNumber][NumObs].mo = month;
2737 wddt[StationNumber][NumObs].dy = day;
2738 wddt[StationNumber][NumObs].hr = hour;
2739 wddt[StationNumber][NumObs].ws = windspd;
2740 wddt[StationNumber][NumObs].wd = winddir;
2741 wddt[StationNumber][NumObs].cl = cloudy;
2742
2743 if (month == 13)
2744 {
2745 FirstMonth[StationNumber].wnd = wddt[StationNumber][0].mo;
2746 LastMonth[StationNumber].wnd = wddt[StationNumber][NumObs - 1].mo;
2747 FirstDay[StationNumber].wnd = wddt[StationNumber][0].dy;
2748 LastDay[StationNumber].wnd = wddt[StationNumber][NumObs - 1].dy;
2749 FirstHour[StationNumber].wnd = wddt[StationNumber][0].hr;
2750 LastHour[StationNumber].wnd = wddt[StationNumber][NumObs - 1].hr;
2751 }
2752
2753 return 1;
2754 }
2755
2756 return 0;
2757}

2890
2891long SetWeatherData(long StationNumber, long NumObs, long month, long day,
2892 double rain, long time1, long time2, double temp1, double temp2,
2893 long humid1, long humid2, double elevation, long tr1, long tr2)
2894{
2895 if (NumObs < MaxWeatherObs[StationNumber])
2896 {
2897 wtrdt[StationNumber][NumObs].mo = month;
2898 wtrdt[StationNumber][NumObs].dy = day;
2899 wtrdt[StationNumber][NumObs].rn = rain;
2900 wtrdt[StationNumber][NumObs].t1 = time1;
2901 wtrdt[StationNumber][NumObs].t2 = time2;
2902 wtrdt[StationNumber][NumObs].T1 = temp1;
2903 wtrdt[StationNumber][NumObs].T2 = temp2;
2904 wtrdt[StationNumber][NumObs].H1 = humid1;
2905 wtrdt[StationNumber][NumObs].H2 = humid2;
2906 wtrdt[StationNumber][NumObs].el = elevation;
2907 wtrdt[StationNumber][NumObs].tr1 = tr1;
2908 wtrdt[StationNumber][NumObs].tr2 = tr2;
2909
2910 if (month == 13)
2911 {
2912 FirstMonth[StationNumber].wtr = wtrdt[StationNumber][0].mo;
2913 LastMonth[StationNumber].wtr = wtrdt[StationNumber][NumObs - 1].mo;
2914 FirstDay[StationNumber].wtr = wtrdt[StationNumber][0].dy;
2915 LastDay[StationNumber].wtr = wtrdt[StationNumber][NumObs - 1].dy;
2916 FirstHour[StationNumber].wtr = wtrdt[StationNumber][0].t1;
2917 LastHour[StationNumber].wtr = wtrdt[StationNumber][NumObs - 1].t2;
2918 }
2919
2920 EnvtChanged[0][StationNumber] = true; // 1hr fuels
2921 EnvtChanged[1][StationNumber] = true; // 10hr fuels
2922 EnvtChanged[2][StationNumber] = true; // 100hr fuels
2923 EnvtChanged[3][StationNumber] = true; // 1000hr fuels
2924 return 1;
2925 }
2926
2927 return 0;
2928}

3038
3039long GetMoistCalcInterval(long FM_SIZECLASS, long CATEGORY)
3040{
3041 return MoistCalcInterval[FM_SIZECLASS][CATEGORY];
3042}
3043
3044
3045void SetMoistCalcInterval(long FM_SIZECLASS, long CATEGORY, long Val)
3046{
3047 switch (CATEGORY)
3048 {
3049 case FM_INTERVAL_TIME:
3050 switch (FM_SIZECLASS)
3051 {
3052 case 1:
3053 if (Val < 60)
3054 Val = 60;
3055 if (Val > 240)
3056 Val = 240;
3057 break;
3058 case 2:
3059 if (Val < 60)
3060 Val = 600;
3061 if (Val > 240)
3062 Val = 240;
3063 break;
3064 case 3:
3065 if (Val < 60)
3066 Val = 6000;
3067 if (Val > 240)
3068 Val = 240;
3069 break;
3070 }
3071 break;
3072 case FM_INTERVAL_ELEV:
3073 if (Val < 10)
3074 Val = 10;
3075 break;
3076 case FM_INTERVAL_SLOPE:
3077 if (Val < 5)
3078 Val = 5;
3079 break;
3080 case FM_INTERVAL_ASP:
3081 if (Val < 5)
3082 Val = 5;
3083 break;
3084 case FM_INTERVAL_COV:
3085 if (Val < 5)
3086 Val = 5;
3087 break;
3088 }
3089 MoistCalcInterval[FM_SIZECLASS][CATEGORY] = Val;
3090}

3149
3150void AllocStationGrid(long XDim, long YDim)
3151{
3152 long x, y, Num;
3153
3154 FreeStationGrid();
3155 size_t nmemb = 2 * XDim* YDim;
3156 grid.XDim = XDim;
3157 grid.YDim = YDim;
3158 grid.Width = ((double) (GetHiEast() - GetLoEast())) / ((double) XDim);
3159 grid.Height = ((double) (GetHiNorth() - GetLoNorth())) / ((double) YDim);
3160 grid.Grid = new long[nmemb];
3161 for (y = 0; y < YDim; y++)
3162 {
3163 for (x = 0; x < XDim; x++) // initialize grid to station 1
3164 {
3165 Num = x + y * grid.XDim;
3166 grid.Grid[Num] = 1;
3167 }
3168 }
3169}
3170
3171
3172long FreeStationGrid()
3173{
3174 if (grid.Grid)
3175 {
3176 delete[] grid.Grid;
3177 grid.Grid = 0;
3178
3179 return 1;
3180 }
3181 grid.Grid = 0;
3182
3183 return 0;
3184}
3185
3186
3187long GetStationNumber(double xpt, double ypt)
3188{
3189 long XCell = (long)((xpt - GetLoEast()) / grid.Width);
3190 long YCell = (long)((ypt - GetLoNorth()) / grid.Height);
3191 long CellNum = XCell + YCell* grid.XDim;
3192
3193 if (grid.Grid[CellNum] > NumWeatherStations) // check to see if data exist
3194 return 0; // for a given weather station
3195 if (grid.Grid[CellNum] > NumWindStations)
3196 return 0;
3197
3198 return grid.Grid[CellNum];
3199}

3205 if (StationNumber <= NumWeatherStations &&
3206 StationNumber <= NumWindStations &&
3207 StationNumber > 0)
3208 grid.Grid[CellNumber] = StationNumber;
3209 else
3210 return 0;
3211
3212 return 1;
3213}

3407void LandscapeTheme::CopyStats(long layer)

3418
3419
3420void LandscapeTheme::FillCats()
3421{
3422 long i, j, k, m, pos;
3423 double x, y, resx, resy;
3424 celldata cell;
3425 crowndata cfuel;
3426 grounddata gfuel;
3427
3428 resx = GetCellResolutionX();
3429 resy = GetCellResolutionY();
3430 for (m = 0; m < 10; m++)
3431 {
3432 maxval[m] = -1e100;
3433 minval[m] = 1e100;
3434 NumAllCats[m] = 0;
3435 for (k = 0; k < 100; k++)
3436 AllCats[m][k] = -1;
3437 }
3438 for (i = 0; i < GetNumNorth(); i++)
3439 {
3440 y = GetHiNorth() - i * resy - resy / 2.0;
3441 for (j = 0; j < GetNumEast(); j++)
3442 {
3443 x = GetLoEast() + j * resx + resx / 2.0;
3444 CellData(x, y, cell, cfuel, gfuel, &pos);
3445 AllCats[0][NumAllCats[0]] = cell.e;
3446 AllCats[1][NumAllCats[1]] = cell.s;
3447 AllCats[2][NumAllCats[2]] = cell.a;
3448 AllCats[3][NumAllCats[3]] = cell.f;
3449 AllCats[4][NumAllCats[4]] = cell.c;
3450 if (HaveCrownFuels())
3451 {
3452 if (cfuel.h >= 0)
3453 AllCats[5][NumAllCats[5]] = cfuel.h;
3454 if (cfuel.b >= 0)
3455 AllCats[6][NumAllCats[6]] = cfuel.b;
3456 if (cfuel.p >= 0)
3457 AllCats[7][NumAllCats[7]] = cfuel.p;
3458 }
3459 if (HaveGroundFuels())
3460 {
3461 if (gfuel.d >= 0)
3462 AllCats[8][NumAllCats[8]] = gfuel.d;
3463 if (gfuel.w >= 0)
3464 AllCats[9][NumAllCats[9]] = gfuel.w;
3465 }
3466 for (m = 0; m < 10; m++)
3467 {
3468 if (maxval[m] < AllCats[m][NumAllCats[m]])
3469 maxval[m] = AllCats[m][NumAllCats[m]];
3470 if (AllCats[m][NumAllCats[m]] >= 0)
3471 {
3472 if (minval[m] > AllCats[m][NumAllCats[m]])
3473 minval[m] = AllCats[m][NumAllCats[m]];
3474 }
3475 }
3476 for (m = 0; m < 10; m++)
3477 {
3478 if (NumAllCats[m] > 98)
3479 continue;
3480 for (k = 0; k < NumAllCats[m]; k++)
3481 {
3482 if (AllCats[m][NumAllCats[m]] == AllCats[m][k])
3483 break;
3484 }
3485 if (k == NumAllCats[m])
3486 NumAllCats[m]++;
3487 }
3488 }
3489 }
3490 for (m = 0; m < 10; m++)
3491 {
3492 if (NumAllCats[m] > 98)
3493 NumAllCats[m] = -1;
3494 }
3495}
3496
3497
3498void LandscapeTheme::SortCats()
3499{
3500 long i, j, m;
3501 long SwapCats[101];
3502
3503 for (m = 0; m < 10; m++)
3504 {
3505 if (NumAllCats[m] < 0)
3506 continue;
3507 memcpy(SwapCats, AllCats[m], 100 * sizeof(long));
3508 for (i = 0; i < NumAllCats[m] - 1; i++)
3509 {
3510 for (j = i + 1; j < NumAllCats[m]; j++)
3511 {
3512 if (SwapCats[j] < SwapCats[i])
3513 {
3514 SwapCats[100] = SwapCats[i];
3515 SwapCats[i] = SwapCats[j];
3516 SwapCats[j] = SwapCats[100];
3517 }
3518 }
3519 }
3520 AllCats[m][0] = 0;
3521 for (i = 0; i < NumAllCats[m]; i++)
3522 AllCats[m][i + 1] = SwapCats[i];
3523 minval[m] = AllCats[m][1];
3524 if (minval[m] < 0)
3525 minval[m] = 0;
3526 }
3527}

3547
3548bool RasterTheme::SetTheme(char* FileName)
3549{
3550 long i, j;
3551 char TestRead[30];
3552 double value;
3553 FILE* Rast;
3554
3555 if ((Rast = fopen(FileName, "r")) == NULL)
3556 return false;
3557
3558 if (map)
3559 delete[] map;
3560 map = 0;
3561 strcpy(Name, FileName);
3562
3563 rMaxVal = 1e-300;
3564 rMinVal = 1e300;
3565 fscanf(Rast, "%s", TestRead);
3566 if (!strcmp(TestRead, "north:")) // GRASS File
3567 {
3568 fscanf(Rast, "%lf", &rN);
3569 fscanf(Rast, "%s", TestRead);
3570 fscanf(Rast, "%lf", &rS);
3571 fscanf(Rast, "%s", TestRead);
3572 fscanf(Rast, "%lf", &rE);
3573 fscanf(Rast, "%s", TestRead);
3574 fscanf(Rast, "%lf", &rW);
3575 fscanf(Rast, "%s", TestRead);
3576 fscanf(Rast, "%ld", &rRows);
3577 fscanf(Rast, "%s", TestRead);
3578 fscanf(Rast, "%ld", &rCols);
3579 rCellSizeY = (rN - rS) / (double) rRows;
3580 rCellSizeX = (rE - rW) / (double) rCols;
3581 }
3582 else if (!strcmp(strupr(TestRead), "NCOLS")) // ARC grid file
3583 {
3584 fscanf(Rast, "%ld", &rCols);
3585 fscanf(Rast, "%s", TestRead);
3586 fscanf(Rast, "%ld", &rRows);
3587 fscanf(Rast, "%s", TestRead);
3588 fscanf(Rast, "%lf", &rW);
3589 fscanf(Rast, "%s", TestRead);
3590 fscanf(Rast, "%lf", &rS);
3591 fscanf(Rast, "%s", TestRead);
3592 fscanf(Rast, "%lf", &rCellSizeX);
3593 fscanf(Rast, "%s", TestRead);
3594 fscanf(Rast, "%s", TestRead);
3595 rN = rS + rCellSizeX * (double) rRows;
3596 rE = rW + rCellSizeX * (double) rCols;
3597 rCellSizeY = rCellSizeX;
3598 }
3599
3600 if ((map = new double[rRows * rCols]) == NULL)
3601 return false;
3602// ZeroMemory(map, rRows * rCols * sizeof(double));
3603 memset(map,0x0, rRows * rCols * sizeof(double));
3604
3605 for (i = 0; i < rRows; i++)
3606 {
3607 for (j = 0; j < rCols; j++)
3608 {
3609 fscanf(Rast, "%lf", &value);
3610 map[i * rCols + j] = value;
3611 if (value >= 0.0)
3612 {
3613 if (value < rMinVal)
3614 rMinVal = value;
3615 if (value > rMaxVal)
3616 rMaxVal = value;
3617 }
3618 }
3619 }
3620 fclose(Rast);
3621
3622 if (CheckCellResUnits() == 2)
3623 {
3624 //rE*=1000.0;
3625 //rW*=1000.0;
3626 //rN*=1000.0;
3627 //rS*=1000.0;
3628 rCellSizeX *= 1000.0;
3629 rCellSizeY *= 1000.0;
3630 }
3631
3632 rW = ConvertUtmToEastingOffset(rW);
3633 rE = ConvertUtmToEastingOffset(rE);
3634 rN = ConvertUtmToNorthingOffset(rN);
3635 rS = ConvertUtmToNorthingOffset(rS);
3636
3637 Continuous = 1;
3638 FillCats();
3639 SortCats();
3640 //ramp = 0;
3641 RedVal = 50;
3642 GreenVal = 0;
3643 BlueVal = 0;
3644 VarVal = 0;
3645 NumColors = 12;
3646 MaxBrite = 255;
3647 OnOff = true;
3648 WantNewRamp = true;
3649 WantNewColor = false;
3650 CreateRamp();
3651
3652 return true;
3653}
3654
3655
3656void RasterTheme::FillCats()
3657{
3658 NumCats = 0;
3659 long i, j, k, m;
3660 double Int;
3661
3662 for (i = 0; i < rRows; i++)
3663 {
3664 for (j = 0; j < rCols; j++)
3665 {
3666 m = i * rCols + j;
3667 modf(map[m], &Int);
3668 if (Int >= 0.0)
3669 {
3670 Cats[NumCats] = (long)ceil(map[m]);
3671 for (k = 0; k < NumCats; k++)
3672 {
3673 if (Cats[NumCats] == Cats[k])
3674 break;
3675 }
3676 if (k == NumCats)
3677 NumCats++;
3678 }
3679 if (NumCats > 99)
3680 break;
3681 }
3682 if (NumCats > 99)
3683 {
3684 NumCats = -1;
3685
3686 break;
3687 }
3688 }
3689 MaxVal = rMaxVal; // base class copies
3690 MinVal = rMinVal;
3691}
3692
3693
3694void RasterTheme::SortCats()
3695{
3696 if (NumCats == -1)
3697 return;
3698 else
3699 CatsOK = 1;
3700 long i, j, SwapCats[101];
3701
3702 memcpy(SwapCats, Cats, 100 * sizeof(long));
3703 for (i = 0; i < NumCats - 1; i++)
3704 {
3705 for (j = i + 1; j < NumCats; j++)
3706 {
3707 if (SwapCats[j] < SwapCats[i])
3708 {
3709 SwapCats[100] = SwapCats[i];
3710 SwapCats[i] = SwapCats[j];
3711 SwapCats[j] = SwapCats[100];
3712 }
3713 }
3714 }
3715 Cats[0] = 0;
3716 for (i = 0; i < NumCats; i++)
3717 Cats[i + 1] = SwapCats[i];
3718}

3720
3721static long ThemeID = 0;
3722static long NumThemes = 0;
3723
3724Themes* FirstTheme = 0;
3725Themes* CurrentTheme;
3726Themes* NextTheme;
3727Themes* LastTheme;
3728
3729
3730double QueryRasterMap(Themes* theme, double xcoord, double ycoord)
3731{
3732 if (theme->theme->map == NULL) //theme->theme->MapAlloc==false) //*
3733 return -2;
3734 if (xcoord<(theme->theme->rW) || (xcoord>theme->theme->rE))
3735 return -3;
3736 if (ycoord<(theme->theme->rS) || (ycoord>theme->theme->rN))
3737 return -4;
3738
3739 double xpt, ypt;
3740 long easti, northi, posit;
3741
3742 xpt = (xcoord - (theme->theme->rW)) / (theme->theme->rCellSizeX);
3743 ypt = (ycoord - (theme->theme->rS)) / (theme->theme->rCellSizeY);
3744 easti = ((long) xpt);
3745 northi = ((long) ypt);
3746 northi = theme->theme->rRows - northi - 1;
3747 if (northi < 0)
3748 northi = 0;
3749 posit = northi * (theme->theme->rCols) + easti;
3750
3751 return theme->theme->map[posit];
3752}

3764 ThemeID = 0; // reset Unique Theme ID
3765
3766 return NumThemes;
3767}
3768
3769Themes* GetRasterTheme(long Num)
3770{
3771 long i;
3772
3773 CurrentTheme = FirstTheme;
3774 for (i = 0; i < NumThemes; i++)
3775 {
3776 NextTheme = (Themes *) CurrentTheme->next;
3777 if (CurrentTheme->ID == Num)
3778 break;
3779 CurrentTheme = NextTheme;
3780 }
3781
3782 return CurrentTheme;
3783}
3784
3785Themes* AllocRasterTheme()
3786{
3787 if (FirstTheme == 0)
3788 {
3789 if ((FirstTheme = new Themes) == NULL)
3790 return NULL;
3791
3792 CurrentTheme = FirstTheme;
3793 CurrentTheme->last = 0;
3794 CurrentTheme->next = 0;
3795 LastTheme = 0;
3796 }
3797 else
3798 {
3799 long i;
3800
3801 CurrentTheme = FirstTheme;
3802 for (i = 0; i < NumThemes; i++)
3803 {
3804 LastTheme = CurrentTheme;
3805 NextTheme = (Themes *) CurrentTheme->next;
3806 CurrentTheme = NextTheme;
3807 }
3808 CurrentTheme = new Themes;
3809 CurrentTheme->next = 0;
3810 CurrentTheme->last = (Themes *) LastTheme;
3811 if (LastTheme)
3812 LastTheme->next = (Themes *) CurrentTheme;
3813 }
3814 NumThemes++;
3815 CurrentTheme->Changed = 1;
3816 CurrentTheme->ID = ThemeID++;
3817 CurrentTheme->Selected = true;
3818 CurrentTheme->theme = new RasterTheme();//(RasterTheme *) calloc(1, sizeof(RasterTheme));
3819
3820 return CurrentTheme;
3821}
3822
3823void FreeAllRasterThemes()
3824{
3825 long i;
3826
3827 CurrentTheme = FirstTheme;
3828 for (i = 0; i < NumThemes; i++)
3829 {
3830 NextTheme = (Themes *) CurrentTheme->next;
3831 delete CurrentTheme->theme;
3832 delete CurrentTheme;//GlobalFree(CurrentTheme);//free(CurrentTheme);
3833 CurrentTheme = NextTheme;
3834 }
3835 FirstTheme = 0;
3836 ThemeID = 0;
3837 NumThemes = 0;
3838}
3839
3840void FreeRasterTheme(long Num)
3841{
3842 long i;
3843
3844 CurrentTheme = FirstTheme;
3845 for (i = 0; i < NumThemes; i++)
3846 {
3847 NextTheme = (Themes *) CurrentTheme->next;
3848 if (CurrentTheme->ID == Num)
3849 break;
3850 CurrentTheme = NextTheme;
3851 }
3852 if (CurrentTheme->last)
3853 {
3854 LastTheme = (Themes *) CurrentTheme->last;
3855 LastTheme->next = (Themes *) NextTheme;
3856 }
3857 delete CurrentTheme->theme;
3858 delete CurrentTheme;//GlobalFree(CurrentTheme);//free(CurrentTheme);
3859 if (Num == 0 && NextTheme != NULL)
3860 {
3861 FirstTheme = NextTheme;
3862 FirstTheme->last = 0;
3863 }
3864 // else
3865 // FirstTheme=LastTheme;
3866 NumThemes--;
3867 ThemeID--;
3868 if (NumThemes == 0)
3869 FirstTheme = 0;
3870 CurrentTheme = FirstTheme; // reorder the themes
3871 for (i = 0; i < NumThemes; i++)
3872 {
3873 NextTheme = (Themes *) CurrentTheme->next;
3874 if (CurrentTheme->ID > Num)
3875 CurrentTheme->ID--;
3876 CurrentTheme = NextTheme;
3877 }
3878}

3888static long NumVals;
3889static bool CantAllocLCP = false;
3890
3891void ReadHeader2()
3892{
3893 fseek(landfile, 0, SEEK_SET);
3894 fread(&Header2, sizeof(headdata2), 1, landfile);
3895 // do this incase a version 1.0 file has gotten through
3896 Header.loeast = ConvertUtmToEastingOffset(Header.WestUtm);
3897 Header.hieast = ConvertUtmToEastingOffset(Header.EastUtm);
3898 Header.lonorth = ConvertUtmToNorthingOffset(Header.SouthUtm);
3899 Header.hinorth = ConvertUtmToNorthingOffset(Header.NorthUtm);
3900 // celldata cell;
3901 // fseek(landfile, sizeof(cell), SEEK_CUR);
3902 // OldFilePosition=ftell(landfile); // position of file at end of first record
3903 // OldFilePosition=0;
3904
3905 if (Header2.FOptions == 1 || Header2.FOptions == 3)
3906 NEED_CUST_MODELS = true;
3907 else
3908 NEED_CUST_MODELS = false;
3909 if (Header2.FOptions == 2 || Header2.FOptions == 3)
3910 NEED_CONV_MODELS = true;
3911 else
3912 NEED_CONV_MODELS = false;
3913 HAVE_CUST_MODELS = false;
3914 HAVE_CONV_MODELS = false;
3915 // set raster resolution
3916 RasterCellResolutionX = (Header2.EastUtm - Header2.WestUtm) /
3917 (double) Header2.numeast;
3918 RasterCellResolutionY = (Header2.NorthUtm - Header2.SouthUtm) /
3919 (double) Header2.numnorth;
3920 ViewPortNorth = RasterCellResolutionY * (double) Header2.numnorth +
3921 Header2.lonorth;
3922 ViewPortSouth = Header2.lonorth;
3923 ViewPortEast = RasterCellResolutionX * (double) Header2.numeast +
3924 Header2.loeast;
3925 ViewPortWest = Header2.loeast;
3926 // NumViewNorth=(ViewPortNorth-ViewPortSouth)/Header.YResol;
3927 // NumViewEast=(ViewPortEast-ViewPortWest)/Header.XResol;
3928 double rows, cols;
3929 rows = (ViewPortNorth - ViewPortSouth) / Header2.YResol;
3930 NumViewNorth = (long)rows;
3931 if (modf(rows, &rows) > 0.5)
3932 NumViewNorth++;
3933 cols = (ViewPortEast - ViewPortWest) / Header2.XResol;
3934 NumViewEast = (long)cols;
3935 if (modf(cols, &cols) > 0.5)
3936 NumViewEast++;
3937
3938 if (HaveCrownFuels())
3939 NumVals = 8;
3940 else
3941 NumVals = 5;
3942 CantAllocLCP = false;
3943
3944 if (lcptheme)
3945 {
3946 delete lcptheme;
3947 lcptheme = 0;
3948 }
3949 lcptheme = new LandscapeTheme(true);
3950}

4243
4244bool SetCellData(double x, double y, celldata* cell, crowndata* crown,
4245 grounddata* ground)
4246{
4247 short ldata[10];
4248 long posit;
4249
4250 posit = GetCellPosition(x, y);
4251
4252 if (!CantAllocLCP)
4253 {
4254 memcpy(ldata, &landscape[posit * NumVals], NumVals * sizeof(short));
4255
4256 if (cell != NULL)
4257 memcpy(ldata, cell, 5 * sizeof(short));
4258 if (crown != NULL)
4259 memcpy(&ldata[5], crown, 3 * sizeof(short));
4260 if (ground != NULL)
4261 memcpy(&ldata[8], ground, 2 * sizeof(short));
4262
4263 memcpy(&landscape[posit * NumVals], ldata, NumVals * sizeof(short));
4264 }
4265 else
4266 {
4267 celldata tcell;
4268
4269 CloseEditLandFile();
4270 OpenEditLandFile();
4271 fseek(GetLandFile(), GetHeadSize(), SEEK_SET);
4272 SetFilePosition(0);
4273
4274 if (Header.CrownFuels == 20)
4275 {
4276 if (Header.GroundFuels == 20)
4277 {
4278 fseek(landfile, (posit - OldFilePosition) * sizeof(celldata),
4279 SEEK_CUR);
4280 if (cell != NULL)
4281 {
4282 fseek(landfile,
4283 -(posit - OldFilePosition) * sizeof(celldata),
4284 SEEK_CUR);
4285 fwrite(cell, sizeof(celldata), 1, landfile);
4286 }
4287 }
4288 else
4289 {
4290 fseek(landfile,
4291 (posit - OldFilePosition) * (sizeof(celldata) +
4292 sizeof(grounddata)),
4293 SEEK_CUR);
4294 if (cell != NULL && ground != NULL)
4295 {
4296 fwrite(cell, sizeof(celldata), 1, landfile);
4297 fwrite(ground, sizeof(grounddata), 1, landfile);
4298 }
4299 else if (cell != NULL)
4300 fwrite(cell, sizeof(celldata), 1, landfile);
4301 else if (ground != NULL)
4302 {
4303 fread(&tcell, sizeof(celldata), 1, landfile);
4304 fwrite(ground, sizeof(grounddata), 1, landfile);
4305 }
4306 }
4307 }
4308 else
4309 {
4310 if (Header.GroundFuels == 20) // none
4311 {
4312 fseek(landfile,
4313 (posit - OldFilePosition) * (sizeof(celldata) +
4314 sizeof(crowndata)),
4315 SEEK_CUR);
4316 if (cell != NULL && crown != NULL)
4317 {
4318 fwrite(cell, sizeof(celldata), 1, landfile);
4319 fwrite(crown, sizeof(crowndata), 1, landfile);
4320 }
4321 else if (cell != NULL)
4322 fwrite(cell, sizeof(celldata), 1, landfile);
4323 else if (crown != NULL)
4324 {
4325 fread(&tcell, sizeof(celldata), 1, landfile);
4326 fwrite(crown, sizeof(crowndata), 1, landfile);
4327 }
4328 }
4329 else
4330 {
4331 fseek(landfile,
4332 (posit - OldFilePosition) * (sizeof(celldata) +
4333 sizeof(crowndata) +
4334 sizeof(grounddata)),
4335 SEEK_CUR);
4336 if (cell != NULL && crown != NULL && ground != NULL)
4337 {
4338 fwrite(cell, sizeof(celldata), 1, landfile);
4339 fwrite(crown, sizeof(crowndata), 1, landfile);
4340 fwrite(ground, sizeof(grounddata), 1, landfile);
4341 }
4342 else if (cell != NULL && crown != NULL)
4343 {
4344 fwrite(cell, sizeof(celldata), 1, landfile);
4345 fwrite(crown, sizeof(crowndata), 1, landfile);
4346 }
4347 else if (cell != NULL && ground != NULL)
4348 {
4349 fwrite(cell, sizeof(celldata), 1, landfile);
4350 fread(&tcell, sizeof(crowndata), 1, landfile);
4351 fwrite(ground, sizeof(grounddata), 1, landfile);
4352 }
4353 else if (crown != NULL && ground != NULL)
4354 {
4355 fread(&tcell, sizeof(celldata), 1, landfile);
4356 fwrite(crown, sizeof(crowndata), 1, landfile);
4357 fwrite(ground, sizeof(grounddata), 1, landfile);
4358 }
4359 else if (cell != NULL)
4360 fwrite(cell, sizeof(celldata), 1, landfile);
4361 else if (crown != NULL)
4362 {
4363 fread(&tcell, sizeof(celldata), 1, landfile);
4364 fwrite(crown, sizeof(crowndata), 1, landfile);
4365 }
4366 else if (ground != NULL)
4367 {
4368 fread(&tcell, sizeof(celldata), 1, landfile);
4369 fread(&tcell, sizeof(crowndata), 1, landfile);
4370 fwrite(ground, sizeof(grounddata), 1, landfile);
4371 }
4372 }
4373 }
4374
4375 CloseEditLandFile();
4376 ReOpenLandFile(); // doesent alloc memory
4377 }
4378
4379 return true;
4380}
4381
4382
4383void GetCellDataFromMemory(long posit, celldata& cell, crowndata& cfuel,
4384 grounddata& gfuel)
4385{
4386 short ldata[10];
4387
4388 memcpy(ldata, &landscape[posit * NumVals], NumVals * sizeof(short));
4389 switch (NumVals)
4390 {
4391 case 5:
4392 // only 5 basic themes
4393 memcpy(&cell, ldata, NumVals * sizeof(short));
4394 break;
4395 case 7:
4396 // 5 basic and duff and woody
4397 memcpy(&cell, ldata, 5 * sizeof(short));
4398 memcpy(&gfuel, &ldata[5], 2 * sizeof(short));
4399 break;
4400 case 8:
4401 // 5 basic and crown fuels
4402 memcpy(&cell, ldata, 5 * sizeof(short));
4403 memcpy(&cfuel, &ldata[5], 3 * sizeof(short));
4404 break;
4405 case 10:
4406 // 5 basic, crown fuels, and duff and woody
4407 memcpy(&cell, ldata, 5 * sizeof(short));
4408 memcpy(&cfuel, &ldata[5], 3 * sizeof(short));
4409 memcpy(&gfuel, &ldata[8], 2 * sizeof(short));
4410 break;
4411 }
4412}

4439 NumVals*Header.numeast, landfile);
4440 fseek(landfile, headsize, SEEK_SET);
4441 OldFilePosition=0;
4442 CantAllocLCP=false;
4443 }
4444 else
4445 CantAllocLCP=true;
4446 }
4447 }
4448 if(CantAllocLCP)
4449 return false;
4450
4451 long Posit;
4452
4453 if(row<0)
4454 row=0;
4455 else if(row>Header.numnorth-1)
4456 row=Header.numnorth-1;
4457 if(col<0)
4458 col=0;
4459 else if(col>Header.numeast-1)
4460 col=Header.numeast-1;
4461
4462 Posit=(row*Header.numeast+col);
4463 if(Posit+num>=Header.numeast*Header.numnorth)
4464 num=Header.numeast*Header.numnorth-Posit-1;
4465 Posit*=NumVals;
4466 memcpy(data, &landscape[Posit], NumVals*num*sizeof(short));
4467
4468 return true;
4469}
4470
4471*/
4472
4473bool SaveLCPMemoryToFile(char* NewName)
4474{
4475 FILE* otpfile;
4476 long i, j, posit;
4477
4478 otpfile = fopen(NewName, "wb");
4479 fwrite(&Header, sizeof(headdata), 1, otpfile);
4480 for (i = 0; i < Header.numnorth; i++)
4481 {
4482 for (j = 0; j < Header.numeast; j++)
4483 {
4484 posit = (i * Header.numeast + j) * NumVals;
4485 fwrite(&landscape[posit], NumVals * sizeof(short), 1, otpfile);
4486 }
4487 }
4488 fclose(otpfile);
4489
4490 return true;
4491}

4493
4494bool WriteAsciiLCPTheme(long ThemeNum, long Type, char* Name)
4495{
4496 FILE* otpfile;
4497 double mult = 1.0;
4498 long i, j, ThemeLoc = ThemeNum;
4499 short val[10];
4500 unsigned long loc;
4501
4502 otpfile = fopen(Name, "w");
4503 printf("Test2\n");
4504 switch (Type)
4505 {
4506 case 1:
4507 // grid
4508 fprintf(otpfile, "%s %ld\n", "NCOLS", Header.numeast);
4509 fprintf(otpfile, "%s %ld\n", "NROWS", Header.numnorth);
4510 fprintf(otpfile, "%s %lf\n", "XLLCORNER", Header.WestUtm);//*MetersToKm);
4511 fprintf(otpfile, "%s %lf\n", "YLLCORNER", Header.SouthUtm);//*MetersToKm);
4512 fprintf(otpfile, "%s %lf\n", "CELLSIZE", Header.XResol);//*MetersToKm
4513 fprintf(otpfile, "%s %ld\n", "NODATA_VALUE", -1L);
4514 break;
4515 case 2:
4516 // grass
4517 fprintf(otpfile, "%s %lf\n", "north:", Header.NorthUtm);//*MetersToKm);
4518 fprintf(otpfile, "%s %lf\n", "south:", Header.SouthUtm);//*MetersToKm);
4519 fprintf(otpfile, "%s %lf\n", "east:", Header.EastUtm);//*MetersToKm);
4520 fprintf(otpfile, "%s %lf\n", "west:", Header.WestUtm);//*MetersToKm);
4521 fprintf(otpfile, "%s %ld\n", "rows:", Header.numnorth);
4522 fprintf(otpfile, "%s %ld\n", "cols:", Header.numeast);
4523 break;
4524 }
4525 if (NumVals == 7)
4526 ThemeLoc -= 3;
4527
4528 if (landscape == 0)
4529 {
4530 fseek(landfile, headsize, SEEK_SET);
4531 SetFilePosition(0);
4532 }
4533
4534 if (ThemeNum == 5 || ThemeNum == 6) // crown height and base height
4535 {
4536 switch (ThemeNum)
4537 {
4538 case 5:
4539 if (Header.HUnits == 1 || Header.HUnits == 2)
4540 mult = 10.0;
4541 break;
4542 case 6:
4543 if (Header.BUnits == 1 || Header.BUnits == 2)
4544 mult = 10.0;
4545 break;
4546 }
4547
4548 for (i = 0; i < Header.numnorth; i++)
4549 {
4550 for (j = 0; j < Header.numeast; j++)
4551 {
4552 if (landscape)
4553 {
4554 loc = (i * Header.numeast + j) * NumVals + ThemeLoc;
4555 fprintf(otpfile, "%4.1lf ", landscape[loc] / mult);
4556 }
4557 else
4558 {
4559 fread(val, NumVals * sizeof(short), 1, landfile);
4560 fprintf(otpfile, "%4.1lf ", (double) val[ThemeNum] / mult);
4561 }
4562 }
4563 fprintf(otpfile, "\n");
4564 }
4565 fclose(otpfile);
4566 }
4567 else if (ThemeNum == 7) // bulk density
4568 {
4569 if (Header.PUnits == 1)
4570 mult = 100.0;
4571 else if (Header.PUnits == 2)
4572 mult = 1000.0;
4573 for (i = 0; i < Header.numnorth; i++)
4574 {
4575 for (j = 0; j < Header.numeast; j++)
4576 {
4577 if (landscape)
4578 {
4579 loc = (i * Header.numeast + j) * NumVals + ThemeLoc;
4580 fprintf(otpfile, "%1.4lf ", landscape[loc] / mult);
4581 }
4582 else
4583 {
4584 fread(val, NumVals * sizeof(short), 1, landfile);
4585 fprintf(otpfile, "%4.1lf ", (double) val[ThemeNum] / mult);
4586 }
4587 }
4588 fprintf(otpfile, "\n");
4589 }
4590 fclose(otpfile);
4591 }
4592 else
4593 {
4594 for (i = 0; i < Header.numnorth; i++)
4595 {
4596 for (j = 0; j < Header.numeast; j++)
4597 {
4598 if (landscape)
4599 {
4600 loc = (i * Header.numeast + j) * NumVals + ThemeLoc;
4601 fprintf(otpfile, "%d ", landscape[loc]);
4602 }
4603 else
4604 {
4605 fread(val, NumVals * sizeof(short), 1, landfile);
4606 fprintf(otpfile, "%4.1lf ", (double) val[ThemeNum] / mult);
4607 }
4608 }
4609 fprintf(otpfile, "\n");
4610 }
4611 fclose(otpfile);
4612 }
4613
4614 if (landscape == 0)
4615 {
4616 fseek(landfile, headsize, SEEK_SET);
4617 SetFilePosition(0);
4618 }
4619
4620 return true;
4621}
4622
4623
4624celldata CellData(double east, double north, celldata& cell, crowndata& cfuel,
4625 grounddata& gfuel, long* posit)
4626{
4627 long Position;
4628 long j;
4629 int16_t shortemp;
4630 if (landscape == 0)
4631 {
4632 if (CantAllocLCP == false)
4633 {
4634 long i;
4635 double AllocSize;
4636 printf("headsize:%d\n",headsize);
4637 fseek(landfile, headsize, SEEK_SET);
4638 AllocSize = Header.numnorth * Header.numeast * NumVals;
4639 if (AllocSize > 2147483647)
4640 {
4641 CantAllocLCP = true;
4642 }
4643 else
4644 {
4645 try
4646 {
4647 landscape = new short[Header.numnorth * Header.numeast * NumVals];
4648 }
4649 catch (...)
4650 {
4651 CantAllocLCP = true;
4652 landscape = 0;
4653 }
4654 if (landscape != NULL)
4655 {
4656 //ZeroMemory(landscape,Header.numnorth * Header.numeast * NumVals * sizeof(short));
4657 memset(landscape,0x0,Header.numnorth * Header.numeast * NumVals * sizeof(short));
4658 for (i = 0; i < Header.numnorth; i++){
4659 //fread(&landscape[i * NumVals * Header.numeast],sizeof(short), NumVals * Header.numeast, landfile);
4660 for (j = 0 ;j < NumVals * Header.numeast;j++)
4661 fread(&shortemp,sizeof(int16_t), 1, landfile);
4662 landscape[i * j] = (short) shortemp;
4663 }
4664 fseek(landfile, headsize, SEEK_SET);
4665 // OldFilePosition=0; // thread local
4666 CantAllocLCP = false;
4667 }
4668 else
4669 CantAllocLCP = true;
4670 }
4671 }
4672 }
4673
4674 Position = GetCellPosition(east, north);
4675 if (!CantAllocLCP)
4676 {
4677 GetCellDataFromMemory(Position, cell, cfuel, gfuel);
4678
4679 return cell;
4680 }
4681
4682 if (Header.CrownFuels == 20)
4683 {
4684 if (Header.GroundFuels == 20)
4685 {
4686 fseek(landfile, (Position - OldFilePosition) * sizeof(celldata),
4687 SEEK_CUR);
4688 fread(&cell, sizeof(celldata), 1, landfile);
4689 }
4690 else
4691 {
4692 fseek(landfile,
4693 (Position - OldFilePosition) * (sizeof(celldata) +
4694 sizeof(grounddata)),
4695 SEEK_CUR);
4696 fread(&cell, sizeof(celldata), 1, landfile);
4697 fread(&gfuel, sizeof(grounddata), 1, landfile);
4698 }
4699 }
4700 else
4701 {
4702 if (Header.GroundFuels == 20) // none
4703 {
4704 fseek(landfile,
4705 (Position - OldFilePosition) * (sizeof(celldata) +
4706 sizeof(crowndata)),
4707 SEEK_CUR);
4708 fread(&cell, sizeof(celldata), 1, landfile);
4709 fread(&cfuel, sizeof(crowndata), 1, landfile);
4710 }
4711 else
4712 {
4713 fseek(landfile,
4714 (Position - OldFilePosition) * (sizeof(celldata) +
4715 sizeof(crowndata) +
4716 sizeof(grounddata)),
4717 SEEK_CUR);
4718 fread(&cell, sizeof(celldata), 1, landfile);
4719 fread(&cfuel, sizeof(crowndata), 1, landfile);
4720 fread(&gfuel, sizeof(grounddata), 1, landfile);
4721 }
4722 if (cfuel.h > 0)
4723 {
4724 CanopyChx.Height = (double) cfuel.h / 10.0;
4725 if (Header.HUnits == 2)
4726 CanopyChx.Height /= 3.280839;
4727 }
4728 else
4729 CanopyChx.Height = CanopyChx.DefaultHeight;
4730 if (cfuel.b > 0)
4731 {
4732 CanopyChx.CrownBase = (double) cfuel.b / 10.0;
4733 if (Header.BUnits == 2)
4734 CanopyChx.CrownBase /= 3.280839;
4735 }
4736 else
4737 CanopyChx.CrownBase = CanopyChx.DefaultBase;
4738 if (cfuel.p > 0)
4739 {
4740 if (Header.PUnits == 1)
4741 CanopyChx.BulkDensity = ((double) cfuel.p) / 100.0;
4742 else if (Header.PUnits == 2)
4743 CanopyChx.BulkDensity = ((double) cfuel.p / 1000.0) * 16.01845;
4744 }
4745 else
4746 CanopyChx.BulkDensity = CanopyChx.DefaultDensity;
4747 }
4748
4749 OldFilePosition = Position + 1;
4750 if (posit != NULL)
4751 *posit = Position;
4752
4753 return cell;
4754}
4755
4756
4757long GetCellPosition(double east, double north)
4758{
4759 double xpt = (east - Header.loeast) / GetCellResolutionX();
4760 double ypt = (north - Header.lonorth) / GetCellResolutionY();
4761 long easti = ((long) xpt);
4762 long northi = ((long) ypt);
4763 northi = Header.numnorth - northi - 1;
4764 if (northi < 0)
4765 northi = 0;
4766 long posit = (northi* Header.numeast + easti);
4767
4768 return posit;
4769}

4850
4851double ConvertEastingOffsetToUtm(double input)
4852{
4853 double MetersToKm = 1.0;
4854 double ipart;
4855
4856 if (Header.GridUnits == 2)
4857 MetersToKm = 0.001;
4858
4859 modf(Header.WestUtm / 1000.0, &ipart);
4860
4861 return (input + ipart * 1000.0) * MetersToKm;
4862}
4863
4864double ConvertNorthingOffsetToUtm(double input)
4865{
4866 double MetersToKm = 1.0;
4867 double ipart;
4868
4869 if (Header.GridUnits == 2)
4870 MetersToKm = 0.001;
4871
4872 modf(Header.SouthUtm / 1000.0, &ipart);
4873
4874 return (input + ipart * 1000.0) * MetersToKm;
4875}
4876
4877double ConvertUtmToEastingOffset(double input)
4878{
4879 double KmToMeters = 1.0;
4880 double ipart;
4881
4882 if (Header.GridUnits == 2)
4883 KmToMeters = 1000.0;
4884
4885 modf(Header.WestUtm / 1000.0, &ipart);
4886
4887 return input * KmToMeters - ipart * 1000.0;
4888}
4889
4890double ConvertUtmToNorthingOffset(double input)
4891{
4892 double KmToMeters = 1.0;
4893 double ipart;
4894
4895 if (Header.GridUnits == 2)
4896 KmToMeters = 1000.0;
4897
4898 modf(Header.SouthUtm / 1000.0, &ipart);
4899
4900 return input * KmToMeters - ipart * 1000.0;
4901}

4933
4934long GetConditMinDeficit()
4935{
4936 if (CondPeriod == false)
4937 return 0;
4938
4939 long CondMin;
4940 long StartMin;
4941
4942 CondMin = (GetJulianDays(conditmonth) + conditday) * 1440;// 00:01 on this day
4943 StartMin = (GetJulianDays(startmonth) + startday) * 1440 +
4944 (starthour / 100 * 60) +
4945 startmin;
4946 if (StartMin < CondMin)
4947 StartMin += 365 * 1440;
4948
4949 return StartMin - CondMin;
4950}

4996
4997long GetMaxMonth()
4998{
4999 long maxmonth = LastMonth[0].all;
5000 long numstations = GetNumStations();
5001
5002 for (long i = 0; i < numstations; i++)
5003 {
5004 if (LastMonth[i].all < maxmonth)
5005 maxmonth = LastMonth[i].all;
5006 }
5007
5008 return maxmonth;
5009}
5010
5011long GetMaxDay()
5012{
5013 long i;
5014 long maxday = LastDay[0].all;
5015 long numstations = GetNumStations();
5016 long maxmonth = GetMaxMonth();
5017
5018 for (i = 0; i < numstations; i++)
5019 {
5020 if (LastMonth[i].all == maxmonth && maxday > LastDay[i].all)
5021 maxday = LastDay[i].all;
5022 }
5023
5024 return maxday;
5025}
5026
5027long GetMaxHour()
5028{
5029 long i;
5030 long maxhour = LastHour[0].all;
5031 long maxmonth = GetMaxMonth();
5032 long maxday = GetMaxDay();
5033 long numstations = GetNumStations();
5034
5035 for (i = 0; i < numstations; i++)
5036 {
5037 if (LastMonth[i].all == maxmonth && LastDay[i].all == maxday)
5038 {
5039 if (LastHour[i].all < maxhour)
5040 maxhour = LastHour[i].all;
5041 }
5042 }
5043
5044 return maxhour;
5045}

5063
5064long GetMinDay()

5068 long NStat = GetNumStations();
5069 long minmonth = GetMinMonth();
5070
5071 for (i = 0; i < NStat; i++)
5072 {
5073 if (FirstMonth[i].all == minmonth)
5074 {
5075 if (FirstDay[i].all > minday)
5076 minday = FirstDay[i].all;
5077 }
5078 }
5079

5090 long minday = GetMinDay();
5091

5093 {

5095 {
5096 if (FirstHour[i].all > minhour)
5097 minhour = FirstHour[i].all;
5098 }
5099 }
5100
5101 return minhour;

5262
5263bool OpenLandFile()
5264{
5265 // SetCanopyChx(15.0, 4.0, 0.2, 30.0, 100, 2, 1);
5266 if (landfile)
5267 fclose(landfile);
5268 if (landscape)
5269 {
5270 delete[] landscape;//GlobalFree(landscape);//free(landscape);
5271 landscape = 0;
5272 CantAllocLCP = false;
5273 }
5274 if ((landfile = fopen(LandFName, "rb")) == NULL)
5275 {
5276 landfile = 0;
5277
5278 return false;
5279 }
5280
5281 return true;
5282}
5283
5284
5285bool ReOpenLandFile()
5286{
5287 if (landfile)
5288 fclose(landfile);
5289 //if(landscape)
5290 //{ GlobalFree(landscape);//free(landscape);
5291 // landscape=0;
5292 // CantAllocLCP=false;
5293 //}
5294 if ((landfile = fopen(LandFName, "rb")) == NULL)
5295 {
5296 landfile = 0;
5297
5298 return false;
5299 }
5300 fseek(landfile, headsize, SEEK_SET);
5301 OldFilePosition = 0;
5302
5303 return true;
5304}

5306
5307bool OpenEditLandFile()
5308{
5309 if (landfile)
5310 fclose(landfile);
5311 //if(landscape)
5312 //{ GlobalFree(landscape);//free(landscape);
5313 // landscape=0;
5314 //}
5315 CantAllocLCP = true;
5316 if ((landfile = fopen(LandFName, "r+b")) != NULL)
5317 return true;
5318 else
5319 {
5320 //SetFileAttributes(LandFName, FILE_ATTRIBUTE_NORMAL);
5321 chmod(LandFName,S_IRWXO);
5322 landfile = fopen(LandFName, "r+b");
5323 }
5324
5325 return true;
5326}

5329void CloseLandFile()
5330{
5331 if (landscape)
5332 {
5333 delete[] landscape;//GlobalFree(landscape);//free(landscape);
5334 landscape = 0;
5335 }
5336 CantAllocLCP = false;
5337 if (landfile)
5338 fclose(landfile);
5339 if (lcptheme)
5340 {
5341 delete lcptheme;
5342 lcptheme = 0;
5343 }
5344 memset(LandFName, 0x0, sizeof LandFName);
5345 landfile = 0;
5346 CanopyChx.Height = CanopyChx.DefaultHeight;
5347 CanopyChx.CrownBase = CanopyChx.DefaultBase;
5348 CanopyChx.BulkDensity = CanopyChx.DefaultDensity;
5349}

5360
5361bool TestForLCPVersion1()
5362{
5363 long TestCrownFuelValue;
5364
5365 rewind(landfile);
5366 fread(&TestCrownFuelValue, sizeof(long), 1, landfile);
5367 if (TestCrownFuelValue < 10) // v1 LCP file had crown fuel indicator as 0 or 1
5368 return true; // v2 LCP file has crown fuel indicator as 10 or 11
5369
5370 return false;
5371}
5372
5373
5374bool TestForLCPVersion2()
5375{
5376 long TestCrownFuelValue;
5377
5378 rewind(landfile);
5379 fread(&TestCrownFuelValue, sizeof(long), 1, landfile);
5380 if (TestCrownFuelValue > 9 && TestCrownFuelValue < 20) // v1 LCP file had crown fuel indicator as 0 or 1
5381 return true; // v2 LCP file has crown fuel indicator as 10 or 11
5382
5383 return false;
5384}
5385
5386
5387bool ConvertLCPFileToVersion2()
5388{
5389 size_t FileNameLength;
5390 long i, j;
5391 char OldLandFName[256];
5392 FILE* oldlandfile;
5393 celldata cell;
5394 crowndata cfuel;
5395
5396 memset(OldLandFName, 0x0, sizeof(OldLandFName));
5397 FileNameLength = strlen(LandFName);
5398 strncpy(OldLandFName, LandFName, FileNameLength - 4);
5399 strcat(OldLandFName, ".LCP1");
5400 fclose(landfile);
5401 if (rename(LandFName, OldLandFName)!=-1)
5402 {
5403 //-------Change Header Info --------------------------- `
5404 oldlandfile = fopen(OldLandFName, "rb");
5405 fread(&OldHeader, sizeof(oldheaddata), 1, oldlandfile);
5406 Header2.CrownFuels = OldHeader.CrownFuels + 10;
5407 Header2.latitude = OldHeader.latitude;
5408 Header2.loelev = OldHeader.loelev;
5409 Header2.hielev = OldHeader.hielev;
5410 Header2.numeast = OldHeader.numeast;
5411 Header2.numnorth = OldHeader.numnorth;
5412 Header2.EastUtm = OldHeader.EastUtm;
5413 Header2.WestUtm = OldHeader.WestUtm;
5414 Header2.NorthUtm = OldHeader.NorthUtm;
5415 Header2.SouthUtm = OldHeader.SouthUtm;
5416 Header2.loeast = ConvertUtmToEastingOffset(Header.WestUtm);
5417 Header2.hieast = ConvertUtmToEastingOffset(Header.EastUtm);
5418 Header2.lonorth = ConvertUtmToNorthingOffset(Header.SouthUtm);
5419 Header2.hinorth = ConvertUtmToNorthingOffset(Header.NorthUtm);
5420 Header2.GridUnits = OldHeader.GridUnits;
5421 Header2.XResol = OldHeader.XResol;
5422 Header2.YResol = OldHeader.YResol;
5423 Header2.EUnits = OldHeader.EUnits;
5424 Header2.SUnits = OldHeader.SUnits;
5425 Header2.AUnits = OldHeader.AUnits;
5426 Header2.FOptions = OldHeader.FOptions;
5427 Header2.CUnits = OldHeader.CUnits;
5428 Header2.HUnits = OldHeader.HUnits;
5429 Header2.BUnits = OldHeader.BUnits;
5430 Header2.PUnits = OldHeader.PUnits;
5431
5432 if (landfile)
5433 fclose(landfile);
5434 landfile = fopen(LandFName, "wb");
5435 if (landfile == NULL)
5436 {
5437 //SetFileAttributes(LandFName, FILE_ATTRIBUTE_NORMAL);
5438 chmod(LandFName,S_IRWXO);
5439 landfile = fopen(LandFName, "wb");
5440 }
5441 fwrite(&Header2, sizeof(headdata2), 1, landfile);
5442
5443 for (i = 0; i < Header2.numnorth; i++)
5444 {
5445 for (j = 0; j < Header2.numeast; j++)
5446 {
5447 fseek(oldlandfile, 2 * sizeof(long), SEEK_CUR);
5448 fread(&cell, sizeof(celldata), 1, oldlandfile);
5449 fwrite(&cell, sizeof(celldata), 1, landfile);
5450 if (Header.CrownFuels == 11)
5451 {
5452 fread(&cfuel, sizeof(crowndata), 1, oldlandfile);
5453 cfuel.h = (short) (cfuel.h * 10); // increase precision to tenths
5454 cfuel.b = (short) (cfuel.b * 10);
5455 if (Header.PUnits == 2)
5456 cfuel.p = (short) (cfuel.p * 10);
5457 fwrite(&cfuel, sizeof(crowndata), 1, landfile);
5458 }
5459 }
5460 }
5461 fclose(oldlandfile);
5462 fclose(landfile);
5463 if ((landfile = fopen(LandFName, "rb")) == NULL)
5464 {
5465 landfile = 0;
5466
5467 return false;
5468 }
5469
5470 return true;
5471 }
5472 else
5473 return false;
5474}

5476
5477bool ConvertLCPFile2ToVersion4()
5478{
5479 size_t FileNameLength;
5480 long i, j;
5481 char OldLandFName[256];
5482 char BkupLandFName[256] = "";
5483 FILE* oldlandfile;
5484 celldata cell;
5485 crowndata cfuel;
5486
5487 strcpy(BkupLandFName, LandFName);
5488 memset(OldLandFName, 0x0, sizeof(OldLandFName));
5489 FileNameLength = strlen(LandFName);
5490 strncpy(OldLandFName, LandFName, FileNameLength - 4);
5491 strcat(OldLandFName, ".LCP3");
5492 fclose(landfile);
5493 if (rename(LandFName, OldLandFName)!=-1)
5494 {
5495 //-------Change Header Info --------------------------- `
5496 oldlandfile = fopen(OldLandFName, "rb");
5497 fread(&Header2, sizeof(headdata2), 1, oldlandfile);
5498 Header.CrownFuels = Header2.CrownFuels + 10;
5499 Header.latitude = Header2.latitude;
5500 Header.loelev = Header2.loelev;
5501 Header.hielev = Header2.hielev;
5502 Header.numeast = Header2.numeast;
5503 Header.numnorth = Header2.numnorth;
5504 Header.EastUtm = Header2.EastUtm;
5505 Header.WestUtm = Header2.WestUtm;
5506 Header.NorthUtm = Header2.NorthUtm;
5507 Header.SouthUtm = Header2.SouthUtm;
5508 Header.loeast = ConvertUtmToEastingOffset(Header.WestUtm);
5509 Header.hieast = ConvertUtmToEastingOffset(Header.EastUtm);
5510 Header.lonorth = ConvertUtmToNorthingOffset(Header.SouthUtm);
5511 Header.hinorth = ConvertUtmToNorthingOffset(Header.NorthUtm);
5512 //Header.loeast=Header2.loeast;
5513 //Header.hieast=Header2.hieast;
5514 //Header.lonorth=Header2.lonorth;
5515 //Header.hinorth=Header2.hinorth;
5516 Header.GridUnits = Header2.GridUnits;
5517 Header.XResol = Header2.XResol;
5518 Header.YResol = Header2.YResol;
5519 Header.EUnits = Header2.EUnits;
5520 Header.SUnits = Header2.SUnits;
5521 Header.AUnits = Header2.AUnits;
5522 Header.FOptions = Header2.FOptions;
5523 Header.CUnits = Header2.CUnits;
5524 Header.HUnits = Header2.HUnits;
5525 Header.BUnits = Header2.BUnits;
5526 Header.PUnits = Header2.PUnits;
5527 // stuff not found in Version 2.0
5528 Header.DUnits = 0;
5529 Header.WOptions = 0;
5530 Header.GroundFuels = 20; // none
5531 memset(Header.ElevFile, 0x0, sizeof(Header.ElevFile));
5532 memset(Header.SlopeFile, 0x0, sizeof(Header.ElevFile));
5533 memset(Header.AspectFile, 0x0, sizeof(Header.ElevFile));
5534 memset(Header.FuelFile, 0x0, sizeof(Header.ElevFile));
5535 memset(Header.CoverFile, 0x0, sizeof(Header.ElevFile));
5536 memset(Header.HeightFile, 0x0, sizeof(Header.ElevFile));
5537 memset(Header.BaseFile, 0x0, sizeof(Header.ElevFile));
5538 memset(Header.DensityFile, 0x0, sizeof(Header.ElevFile));
5539 memset(Header.DuffFile, 0x0, sizeof(Header.ElevFile));
5540 memset(Header.WoodyFile, 0x0, sizeof(Header.ElevFile));
5541 memset(Header.Description, 0x0, sizeof(Header.Description));
5542
5543 landfile = fopen(LandFName, "wb");
5544 if (landfile == NULL)
5545 {
5546 //SetFileAttributes(LandFName, FILE_ATTRIBUTE_NORMAL);
5547 chmod(LandFName,S_IRWXO);
5548 landfile = fopen(LandFName, "wb");
5549 }
5550 fwrite(&Header, sizeof(headdata), 1, landfile);
5551
5552 for (i = 0; i < Header.numnorth; i++)
5553 {
5554 for (j = 0; j < Header.numeast; j++)
5555 {
5556 fread(&cell, sizeof(celldata), 1, oldlandfile);
5557 fwrite(&cell, sizeof(celldata), 1, landfile);
5558 if (Header.CrownFuels == 21)
5559 {
5560 fread(&cfuel, sizeof(crowndata), 1, oldlandfile);
5561 fwrite(&cfuel, sizeof(crowndata), 1, landfile);
5562 }
5563 }
5564 }
5565 fclose(oldlandfile);
5566 CloseLandFile();
5567
5568 strcpy(LandFName, BkupLandFName);
5569 if (!OpenLandFile())
5570 return false;
5571
5572 ReadHeader();
5573 lcptheme->AnalyzeStats();
5574 Header.numelev = lcptheme->NumAllCats[0];
5575 Header.numslope = lcptheme->NumAllCats[1];
5576 Header.numaspect = lcptheme->NumAllCats[2];
5577 Header.numfuel = lcptheme->NumAllCats[3];
5578 Header.numcover = lcptheme->NumAllCats[4];
5579 Header.numheight = lcptheme->NumAllCats[5];
5580 Header.numbase = lcptheme->NumAllCats[6];
5581 Header.numdensity = lcptheme->NumAllCats[7];
5582 Header.numduff = 0;//lcptheme->NumAllCats[8];
5583 Header.numwoody = 0;//lcptheme->NumAllCats[9];
5584 memcpy(Header.elevs, lcptheme->AllCats[0], 100 * sizeof(long));
5585 memcpy(Header.slopes, lcptheme->AllCats[1], 100 * sizeof(long));
5586 memcpy(Header.aspects, lcptheme->AllCats[2], 100 * sizeof(long));
5587 memcpy(Header.fuels, lcptheme->AllCats[3], 100 * sizeof(long));
5588 memcpy(Header.covers, lcptheme->AllCats[4], 100 * sizeof(long));
5589 memcpy(Header.heights, lcptheme->AllCats[5], 100 * sizeof(long));
5590 memcpy(Header.bases, lcptheme->AllCats[6], 100 * sizeof(long));
5591 memcpy(Header.densities, lcptheme->AllCats[7], 100 * sizeof(long));
5592// ZeroMemory(Header.duffs, 100 * sizeof(long));
5593 memset(Header.duffs,0x0, 100 * sizeof(long));
5594// ZeroMemory(Header.woodies, 100 * sizeof(long));
5595 memset(Header.woodies,0x0, 100 * sizeof(long));
5596 //memcpy(Header.duffs, lcptheme->AllCats[8], 100*sizeof(long));
5597 //memcpy(Header.woodies, lcptheme->AllCats[9], 100*sizeof(long));
5598 Header.loslope = (long)lcptheme->minval[1];
5599 Header.hislope = (long)lcptheme->maxval[1];
5600 Header.loaspect = (long)lcptheme->minval[2];
5601 Header.hiaspect = (long)lcptheme->maxval[2];
5602 Header.lofuel = (long)lcptheme->minval[3];
5603 Header.hifuel = (long)lcptheme->maxval[3];
5604 Header.locover = (long)lcptheme->minval[4];
5605 Header.hicover = (long)lcptheme->maxval[4];
5606 Header.loheight = (long)lcptheme->minval[5];
5607 Header.hiheight = (long)lcptheme->maxval[5];
5608 Header.lobase = (long)lcptheme->minval[6];
5609 Header.hibase = (long)lcptheme->maxval[6];
5610 Header.lodensity = (long)lcptheme->minval[7];
5611 Header.hidensity = (long)lcptheme->maxval[7];
5612 Header.loduff = 0;//lcptheme->minval[8];
5613 Header.hiduff = 0;//lcptheme->maxval[8];
5614 Header.lowoody = 0;//lcptheme->minval[9];
5615 Header.hiwoody = 0;//lcptheme->maxval[9];
5616 CloseLandFile();
5617
5618 strcpy(LandFName, BkupLandFName);
5619 landfile = fopen(LandFName, "rb+");
5620 fwrite(&Header, sizeof(headdata), 1, landfile);
5621 fclose(landfile);
5622 OpenLandFile();
5623
5624 return true;
5625 }
5626 else
5627 return false;
5628}

5882
5883
5884COLORREF ThemeColors::ColorFromSpectrum(long ColorVal)
5885{
5886 COLORREF Colr=RGB(255,255,255);
5887 BYTE Red, Green, Blue;
5888 double RelValue, ColrCat, SubColr;
5889
5890 if(ColorVal>=0.0)
5891 { RelValue=(ColorVal-MinVal)/IntValue;
5892 SubColr=modf(RelValue/50.0, &ColrCat);
5893 if(ColrCat>6)
5894 { ColrCat=6;
5895 SubColr=49.0/50.0;
5896 }
5897 switch(long(ColrCat))
5898 { case 0:
5899 Red=1; Green=1; Blue=1;
5900 break;
5901 case 1:
5902 Red=1; Green=0; Blue=1;
5903 break;
5904 case 2:
5905 Red=0; Green=0; Blue=1;
5906 break;
5907 case 3:
5908 Red=0; Green=1; Blue=1;
5909 break;
5910 case 4:
5911 Red=0; Green=1; Blue=0;
5912 break;
5913 case 5:
5914 Red=1; Green=1; Blue=0;
5915 break;
5916 case 6:
5917 Red=1; Green=0; Blue=0;
5918 break;
5919 }
5920 SubColr*=155; // SubColr*=255
5921 SubColr+=100; // increase between 100 and 255
5922 Colr=GetPaletteColor(Red*SubColr, Green*SubColr, Blue*SubColr);
5923 }
5924
5925 return Colr;
5926}

5940
5941COLORREF GetThemeColor(long VisTheme, long Attrib)
5942{
5943 COLORREF colr;
5944
5945 if(VisTheme<0)
5946 VisTheme=VisibleThemeNumber;
5947
5948 switch(VisTheme)
5949 { case 0: Attrib=(long) ((((double)(Attrib-Header.loelev))/
5950 ((double)(Header.hielev-Header.loelev)))*100);
5951 if(Attrib>99)
5952 Attrib=99;
5953 if(Attrib<0)
5954 Attrib=0;
5955 colr=themecolors.Elevation[Attrib]; break;
5956 case 1: if(Header.SUnits>0) // percent
5957 Attrib/=7;
5958 else // degrees
5959 Attrib/=6;
5960 if(Attrib>17) Attrib=17;
5961 if(Attrib<0)
5962 Attrib=0;
5963 colr=themecolors.Slope[Attrib]; break;
5964 case 2: if(Header.AUnits>0)
5965 { Attrib=(long) ((double) Attrib)/14.4;
5966 if(Attrib>119)
5967 Attrib=119;
5968 }

6180//-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
6181// BurnPeriod Data and Functions
6182//-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
6183
6184static double DownTime = 0.0;
6185static long NumAbsoluteData = 0;
6186static long NumRelativeData = 0;
6187static long LastAccess = -1;
6188static AbsoluteBurnPeriod* abp = 0;
6189static RelativeBurnPeriod* rbp = 0;
6190
6191
6192bool AllocBurnPeriod(long Num)
6193{
6194 FreeBurnPeriod();
6195
6196 //long i, FirstDay, StartDay, EndDay, NumDays, LastDay;
6197 long i,FirstDay, NumDays, LastDay;
6198 //long mo, dy, JDay, maxdy;
6199 long mo, dy, JDay;
6200
6201 FirstDay = GetJulianDays(GetMinMonth());
6202 FirstDay += GetMinDay();
6203 LastDay = GetJulianDays(GetMaxMonth());
6204 LastDay += GetMaxDay();
6205 if (FirstDay < LastDay)
6206 NumDays = LastDay - FirstDay;
6207 else
6208 NumDays = 365 - FirstDay + LastDay;
6209 if (Num < NumDays)
6210 Num = NumDays;
6211
6212 abp = new AbsoluteBurnPeriod[Num];
6213 if (abp == NULL)
6214 return false;
6215 memset(abp, 0x0, Num * sizeof(AbsoluteBurnPeriod));
6216 NumAbsoluteData = Num;
6217
6218 mo = GetMinMonth();
6219 dy = GetMinDay();
6220 for (i = 0; i < NumDays; i++)
6221 {
6222 abp[i].Month = mo;
6223 abp[i].Day = dy;
6224 abp[i].Start = 0;
6225 abp[i].End = 2400;
6226 dy++;
6227 JDay = dy + GetJulianDays(mo);
6228 if (mo < 12)
6229 {
6230 if (JDay > GetJulianDays(mo + 1))
6231 {
6232 dy = 1;
6233 mo++;
6234 }
6235 }
6236 else
6237 {
6238 if (JDay > 365)
6239 {
6240 dy = 1;
6241 mo = 1;
6242 }
6243 }
6244 }
6245
6246 return true;
6247}

6255 delete[] abp; //free(abp);
6256 abp = 0;
6257 if (rbp)
6258 delete[] rbp; //free(rbp);
6259 rbp = 0;
6260 DownTime = 0.0;
6261 LastAccess = -1;
6262}

6273 break;
6274 }
6275 abp[num].Month = mo;
6276 abp[num].Day = dy;
6277 abp[num].Start = start;
6278 abp[num].End = end;
6279 }
6280}

6299 return true;

6308
6309bool InquireInBurnPeriod(double SimTime)
6310{
6311 if (!rbp)
6312 return true;
6313
6314 for (i = LastAccess + 1; i < NumRelativeData; i++)
6315 {
6316 if (SimTime >= rbp[i].Start)
6317 {
6318 if (SimTime <= rbp[i].End)
6319 {
6320 LastAccess = i - 1;
6321
6322 return true;
6323 }
6324 }
6325 else
6326 break;
6327 }
6328
6329 return false;
6330}
6331
6332long GetJulianDays(long Month)
6333{
6334 long days;
6335 switch (Month)
6336 {
6337 case 1:
6338 days = 0; break; // cumulative days to begin of month
6339 case 2:
6340 days = 31; break; // except ignores leapyear, but who cares anyway,
6341 case 3:
6342 days = 59; break;
6343 case 4:
6344 days = 90; break;
6345 case 5:
6346 days = 120; break;
6347 case 6:
6348 days = 151; break;
6349 case 7:
6350 days = 181; break;
6351 case 8:
6352 days = 212; break;
6353 case 9:
6354 days = 243; break;
6355 case 10:
6356 days = 273; break;
6357 case 11:
6358 days = 304; break;
6359 case 12:
6360 days = 334; break;
6361 default:
6362 days = 0; break;
6363 }
6364
6365 return days;
6366}
