6368
6393double ConvertActualTimeToSimtime(long mo, long dy, long hr, long mn,
6394 bool FromCondit)
6395{
6396 double SimTime, RefStart;
6397
6398 if (!FromCondit)
6399 {
6400 if (GetStartDate() == 0)
6401 {
6402 SimTime = -1.0;
6403 return SimTime;
6404 }
6405 RefStart = (GetJulianDays(startmonth) + startday) * 1440.0 +
6406 starthour /
6407 100.0 * 60.0 +
6408 startmin;
6409 }
6410 else
6411 {
6412 if (conditmonth == 0 && conditday == 0)
6413 {
6414 SimTime = -1.0;
6415 return SimTime;
6416 }
6417 RefStart = (GetJulianDays(conditmonth) + conditday) * 1440.0;
6418 }
6419
6420 if (!FromCondit)
6421 {
6422 if (mo >= startmonth)
6423 SimTime = (GetJulianDays(mo) + dy) * 1440.0 +
6424 hr /
6425 100.0 * 60.0 +
6426 mn;
6427 else
6428 SimTime = (GetJulianDays(mo) + dy + 365.0) * 1440.0 +
6429 hr /
6430 100.0 * 60.0 +
6431 mn;
6432 }
6433 else
6434 {
6435 if (mo >= conditmonth)
6436 SimTime = (GetJulianDays(mo) + dy) * 1440.0 +
6437 hr /
6438 100.0 * 60.0 +
6439 mn;
6440 else
6441 SimTime = (GetJulianDays(mo) + dy + 365.0) * 1440.0 +
6442 hr /
6443 100.0 * 60.0 +
6444 mn;
6445 }
6446 SimTime -= RefStart;
6447
6448 return SimTime;
6449}
6450
6451
6452void ConvertSimtimeToActualTime(double SimTime, long* mo, long* dy, long* hr,
6453 long* mn, bool FromCondit)
6454{
6455 long months, days, hours, mins, ndays;
6456 double fday, fhour;
6457
6458 fday = (SimTime / 1440.0); // days from minutes
6459 days = (long) fday;
6460 fhour = ((fday - days) * 24.0); // hours from days
6461 hours = (long) fhour;
6462 mins = (long)((fhour - hours) * 60); // minutes from hours
6463
6464 if (!FromCondit)
6465 {
6466 hours += GetStartHour() / 100;
6467 mins += GetStartMin();
6468 }
6469 if (mins > 60)
6470 {
6471 mins -= 60;
6472 hours++;
6473 }
6474 if (hours >= 24)
6475 {
6476 hours -= 24;
6477 days++;
6478 }
6479 hours *= 100;
6480 if (!FromCondit)
6481 {
6482 if (GetStartDate() + days > 365)
6483 {
6484 days = GetStartDate() + days - 365;
6485 for (i = 1; i < 12; i++)
6486 {
6487 if (days < GetJulianDays(i))
6488 break;
6489 }
6490 days -= GetJulianDays(i - 1);
6491 months = i - 1;
6492 }
6493 else
6494 {
6495 for (i = 1; i < 12; i++)
6496 {
6497 if (GetStartMonth() + i > 12)
6498 ndays = 365 + GetJulianDays(i);
6499 else
6500 ndays = GetJulianDays(GetStartMonth() + i);
6501 if (days + GetStartDate() <= ndays)
6502 break;
6503 }
6504 if (GetStartMonth() + i - 1 > 12)
6505 ndays = 365 + GetJulianDays(i - 1);
6506 else
6507 ndays = GetJulianDays(GetStartMonth() + i - 1);
6508 days -= (ndays - GetStartDate());//(GetJulianDays(GetStartMonth()+i-1)-GetStartDate());
6509 months = GetStartMonth() + (i - 1);
6510 if (months > 12)
6511 months -= 12;
6512 }
6513 }
6514 else
6515 {
6516 long ConDate = GetJulianDays(conditmonth) + conditday;
6517
6518 if (ConDate + days > 365)
6519 {
6520 days = ConDate + days - 365;
6521 for (i = 1; i < 12; i++)
6522 {
6523 if (days < GetJulianDays(i))
6524 break;
6525 }
6526 days -= GetJulianDays(i - 1);
6527 months = i - 1;
6528 }
6529 else
6530 {
6531 for (i = 1; i < 12; i++)
6532 {
6533 if (conditmonth + i > 12)
6534 ndays = 365 + GetJulianDays(i);
6535 else
6536 ndays = GetJulianDays(conditmonth + i);
6537 if (days + ConDate < ndays)//GetJulianDays(conditmonth+i))
6538 break;
6539 }
6540 if (conditmonth + i > 12)
6541 ndays = 365 + GetJulianDays(i - 1);
6542 else
6543 ndays = GetJulianDays(conditmonth + i - 1);
6544 days -= (ndays - ConDate);//(GetJulianDays(conditmonth+i-1)-ConDate);
6545 months = conditmonth + (i - 1);
6546 if (months > 12)
6547 months -= 12;
6548 }
6549 }
6550
6551 *mo = months;
6552 *dy = days;
6553 *hr = hours;
6554 *mn = mins;
6555}

6557
6558bool CheckBurnPeriod(long mo1, long dy1, long mo2, long dy2)
6559{
6560 if (abp == 0)
6561 return true;
6562
6563 long BPStart, BPEnd;
6564 long DurStart, DurEnd;
6565
6566 BPStart = GetJulianDays(abp[0].Month);
6567 BPStart += abp[0].Day;
6568 BPEnd = GetJulianDays(abp[NumAbsoluteData - 1].Month);
6569 BPEnd += abp[NumAbsoluteData - 1].Day;
6570
6571 DurStart = GetJulianDays(mo1);//(startmonth); // comments remove references to stored start and end times
6572 DurStart += dy1;//startday;
6573 DurEnd = GetJulianDays(mo2);//(endmonth);
6574 DurEnd += dy2;//endday;
6575
6576 if (DurEnd < DurStart) // spans new year
6577 {
6578 if (DurStart < BPStart)
6579 return false;
6580 if (DurEnd > BPEnd)
6581 return false;
6582 }
6583 else
6584 {
6585 if (DurStart < BPStart)
6586 return false;
6587 if (DurEnd > BPEnd)
6588 return false;
6589 }
6590
6591 return true;
6592}

6594
6595void ConvertAbsoluteToRelativeBurnPeriod()
6596{
6597 long i, j, days, Day, Month, NumAlloc;
6598 double Add, Begin, End, Start, hrs, mins;
6599 RelativeBurnPeriod* trbp;
6600
6601 if (abp == 0)
6602 return;
6603 if (rbp)
6604 delete[] rbp;//GlobalFree(rbp);//free(rbp);
6605
6606 Start = GetJulianDays(startmonth);
6607 Start += startday - 1;
6608 End = GetJulianDays(endmonth);
6609 End += (long)endday;
6610 if (End < Start)
6611 NumRelativeData = (long)(End + 365 - Start);
6612 else
6613 NumRelativeData = (long)(End - Start);
6614
6615 NumAlloc = NumAbsoluteData;
6616 if (NumRelativeData > NumAbsoluteData)
6617 NumAlloc = NumRelativeData;
6618
6619 rbp = new RelativeBurnPeriod[NumAlloc];
6620 memset(rbp, 0x0, NumAlloc * sizeof(RelativeBurnPeriod));
6621 trbp = new RelativeBurnPeriod[NumAlloc];
6622 memset(trbp, 0x0, NumAlloc * sizeof(RelativeBurnPeriod));
6623
6624 if (NumRelativeData > NumAbsoluteData)
6625 {
6626 AbsoluteBurnPeriod* tabp = new AbsoluteBurnPeriod[NumRelativeData];
6627 memcpy(tabp, abp, NumAbsoluteData * sizeof(AbsoluteBurnPeriod));
6628 delete[] abp;
6629 abp = new AbsoluteBurnPeriod[NumRelativeData];
6630 memcpy(abp, tabp, NumAbsoluteData * sizeof(AbsoluteBurnPeriod));
6631 delete[] tabp;
6632
6633 Month = abp[NumAbsoluteData - 1].Month;
6634 Day = abp[NumAbsoluteData - 1].Day;
6635 for (i = NumAbsoluteData; i < NumRelativeData; i++)
6636 {
6637 Day++;
6638 if (Month < 12)
6639 {
6640 if (Day > GetJulianDays(Month + 1) - GetJulianDays(Month))
6641 {
6642 Day = 1;
6643 Month++;
6644 }
6645 }
6646 else
6647 {
6648 if (Day > 31)
6649 {
6650 Day = 1;
6651 Month = 1;
6652 }
6653 }
6654 abp[i].Month = Month;
6655 abp[i].Day = Day;
6656 abp[i].Start = 0;
6657 abp[i].End = 2400;
6658 }
6659 NumAbsoluteData = NumRelativeData;
6660 }
6661
6662 rbp[0].Start = 0.0;//starthour*0.6;
6663 rbp[0].End = 1440 - starthour * 0.6;
6664 for (i = 1;
6665 i < NumRelativeData;
6666 i++) // initialize all data to minutes
6667 {
6668 rbp[i].Start = rbp[i - 1].End;
6669 rbp[i].End = 1440 * (i + 1) - starthour * 0.6;
6670 }
6671
6672 days = GetJulianDays(abp[0].Month);
6673 days += abp[0].Day - 1;
6674 End = Start = days * 1440;
6675 mins = modf(abp[0].Start / 100.0, &hrs);
6676 Start += (hrs * 60.0 + mins);
6677 mins = modf(abp[0].End / 100.0, &hrs);
6678 End += (hrs * 60.0 + mins);
6679 End -= Start;
6680
6681 trbp[0].Start = 0;
6682 trbp[0].End = End;
6683
6684 for (i = 1; i < NumAbsoluteData; i++)
6685 {
6686 days = GetJulianDays(abp[i].Month);
6687 if (abp[i].Month < abp[0].Month)
6688 days += 365;
6689 days += abp[i].Day - 1;
6690 End = Begin = days * 1440;
6691 mins = modf(abp[i].Start / 100.0, &hrs);
6692 Begin += (hrs * 60.0 + mins);
6693 mins = modf(abp[i].End / 100.0, &hrs);
6694 End += (hrs * 60.0 + mins);
6695 Begin -= Start;
6696 End -= Start;
6697
6698 trbp[i].Start = Begin;
6699 trbp[i].End = End;
6700 }
6701
6702 days = GetJulianDays(startmonth);
6703 days += startday - 1;
6704 if (startmonth < abp[0].Month)
6705 days += 365;
6706 Begin = days * 1440;
6707 mins = modf(starthour / 100.0, &hrs);
6708 Begin += (hrs * 60.0 + mins); // beginning of simulation time
6709
6710 if (trbp[NumAbsoluteData - 1].End + Start < Begin) // if after new year
6711 Add = Begin - (Start + (365 * 1440)); // start of data af
6712 else
6713 Add = Start - Begin; // start of data earlier than begin of simulation
6714
6715 for (i = 0; i < NumAbsoluteData; i++)
6716 {
6717 trbp[i].Start += Add;
6718 trbp[i].End += Add;
6719 }
6720
6721 long FirstDay, StartDay, EndDay, NumDays;// LastDay;
6722
6723 FirstDay = GetJulianDays(GetMinMonth());
6724 FirstDay += GetMinDay();
6725 StartDay = GetJulianDays(GetStartMonth());
6726 StartDay += GetStartDay();
6727 EndDay = GetJulianDays(GetEndMonth());
6728 EndDay += GetEndDay();
6729 if (StartDay < FirstDay)
6730 StartDay += 365;
6731 if (EndDay < FirstDay)
6732 EndDay += 365;
6733
6734 NumDays = EndDay - StartDay;
6735
6736 for (i = 0; i <= NumDays; i++)
6737 {
6738 j = i + StartDay - FirstDay;
6739 if (i < NumAlloc && j < NumAlloc)
6740 rbp[i] = trbp[j];
6741 }
6742
6743 /*
6744 for(i=0; i<NumAbsoluteData; i++)
6745 { for(j=0; j<NumRelativeData; j++)
6746 { if(trbp[i].Start>=rbp[j].Start && trbp[i].End<=rbp[j].End)
6747 rbp[j]=trbp[i];
6748 }
6749 }
6750 */
6751
6752 LastAccess = -1;
6753 // DownTime=0.0;
6754 delete[] trbp;//GlobalFree(trbp);//free(trbp);
6755}

6771//-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
6772// Fuel Moisture Data and Functions
6773//-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
6774
6775static InitialFuelMoisture fm[257];
6776
6777bool SetInitialFuelMoistures(long Model, long t1, long t10, long t100,
6778 long tlh, long tlw)
6779{
6780 if (Model > 256 || Model < 1)
6781 return false;
6782
6783 fm[Model].TL1 = t1;
6784 fm[Model].TL10 = t10;
6785 fm[Model].TL100 = t100;
6786 fm[Model].TLLH = tlh;
6787 fm[Model].TLLW = tlw;
6788
6789 if (t1 > 1 && t10 > 1)
6790 fm[Model].FuelMoistureIsHere = true;
6791 else
6792 fm[Model].FuelMoistureIsHere = false;
6793
6794 long i, j;
6795 for (i = 0; i < 3; i++) // only up to 100 hr fuels [3]
6796 {
6797 for (j = 0; j < 5; j++)
6798 EnvtChanged[i][j] = true;
6799 }
6800
6801 return fm[Model].FuelMoistureIsHere;
6802}
6803
6804bool GetInitialFuelMoistures(long Model, long* t1, long* t10, long* t100,
6805 long* tlh, long* tlw)
6806{
6807 if (Model > 256 || Model < 1)
6808 return false;
6809
6810 if (fm[Model].FuelMoistureIsHere)
6811 {
6812 *t1 = fm[Model].TL1;
6813 *t10 = fm[Model].TL10;
6814 *t100 = fm[Model].TL100;
6815 *tlh = fm[Model].TLLH;
6816 *tlw = fm[Model].TLLW;
6817
6818 return true;
6819 }
6820
6821 return false;
6822}
6823
6824long GetInitialFuelMoisture(long Model, long FuelClass)
6825{
6826 if (Model > 256 || Model < 1)
6827 return 2;
6828
6829 long mx;
6830
6831 switch (FuelClass)
6832 {
6833 case 0:
6834 mx = fm[Model].TL1; break;
6835 case 1:
6836 mx = fm[Model].TL10; break;
6837 case 2:
6838 mx = fm[Model].TL100; break;
6839 case 3:
6840 mx = fm[Model].TLLH; break;
6841 case 4:
6842 mx = fm[Model].TLLW; break;
6843 }
6844
6845 return mx;
6846}
6847
6848bool InitialFuelMoistureIsHere(long Model)
6849{
6850 if (Model > 256 || Model < 1)
6851 return false;
6852
6853 return fm[Model].FuelMoistureIsHere;
6854}

6877
6878bool AllocCoarseWoody(long ModelNumber, long NumClasses)
6879{
6880 if (coarsewoody[ModelNumber - 1].wd)
6881 FreeCoarseWoody(ModelNumber);
6882 if ((coarsewoody[ModelNumber - 1].wd = new WoodyData[NumClasses]) == NULL) //(WoodyData *) GlobalAlloc(GMEM_FIXED | GMEM_ZEROINIT, NumClasses*sizeof(WoodyData)))==NULL)
6883 return false;
6884// ZeroMemory(coarsewoody[ModelNumber - 1].wd, NumClasses * sizeof(WoodyData));
6885 memset(coarsewoody[ModelNumber - 1].wd,0x0, NumClasses * sizeof(WoodyData));
6886 coarsewoody[ModelNumber - 1].NumClasses = NumClasses;
6887 coarsewoody[ModelNumber - 1].TotalWeight = 0.0;
6888// ZeroMemory(coarsewoody[ModelNumber - 1].Description, 64 * sizeof(char));
6889 memset(coarsewoody[ModelNumber - 1].Description,0x0, 64 * sizeof(char));
6890
6891 return true;
6892}

6894
6895void FreeCoarseWoody(long ModelNumber)
6896{
6897 if (coarsewoody[ModelNumber - 1].wd)
6898 delete[] coarsewoody[ModelNumber - 1].wd;//GlobalFree(coarsewoody[ModelNumber-1].wd);//free(coarsewoody[ModelNumber-1].wd);
6899 coarsewoody[ModelNumber - 1].NumClasses = 0;
6900 coarsewoody[ModelNumber - 1].wd = 0;
6901 coarsewoody[ModelNumber - 1].Units = -1;
6902 coarsewoody[ModelNumber - 1].TotalWeight = 0.0;
6903 coarsewoody[ModelNumber - 1].Depth = 0.0;
6904}
6905
6906void FreeAllCoarseWoody()
6907{
6908 long i;
6909
6910 for (i = 1; i < MAXNUM_COARSEWOODY_MODELS + 1; i++)
6911 FreeCoarseWoody(i);
6912 for (i = 0; i < 256; i++)
6913 {
6914 if (NFFLWoody[i].wd)
6915 delete[] NFFLWoody[i].wd;//GlobalFree(NFFLWoody[i].wd);//free(NFFLWoody[i].wd);
6916 NFFLWoody[i].NumClasses = 0;
6917 NFFLWoody[i].wd = 0;
6918 }
6919 if (tempwoody.wd)
6920 delete[] tempwoody.wd;//GlobalFree(tempwoody.wd);//free(tempwoody.wd);
6921}
6922
6923bool SetWoodyData(long ModelNumber, long ClassNumber, WoodyData* wd,
6924 long units)
6925{
6926 if (ModelNumber > MAXNUM_COARSEWOODY_MODELS - 1)
6927 return false;
6928
6929 if (coarsewoody[ModelNumber - 1].NumClasses <= ClassNumber)
6930 return false;
6931
6932 //long i;
6933 double Total = 0.0;
6934
6935 //coarsewoody[ModelNumber-1].TotalWeight=0.0;
6936 memcpy(&coarsewoody[ModelNumber - 1].wd[ClassNumber], wd,
6937 sizeof(WoodyData));
6938 coarsewoody[ModelNumber - 1].Units = units;
6939 //for(i=0; i<=ClassNumber; i++)
6940 Total = coarsewoody[ModelNumber - 1].TotalWeight + wd[0].Load;//coarsewoody[ModelNumber-1].wd[i];
6941 coarsewoody[ModelNumber - 1].TotalWeight = Total;
6942 SetNFFLWoody();
6943 EnvtChanged[3][0] = true;
6944 EnvtChanged[3][1] = true;
6945 EnvtChanged[3][2] = true;
6946 EnvtChanged[3][3] = true;
6947 EnvtChanged[3][4] = true;
6948
6949 return true;
6950}

6952bool SetWoodyDataDepth(long ModelNumber, double depth, const char* Description)
6953{
6954 if (ModelNumber > MAXNUM_COARSEWOODY_MODELS - 1)
6955 return false;
6956
6957 coarsewoody[ModelNumber - 1].Depth = depth;
6958 memcpy(coarsewoody[ModelNumber - 1].Description, Description,
6959 64 * sizeof(char));
6960
6961 return true;
6962}

7241 // if((NFFLWoody[11].wd=(WoodyData *) GlobalAlloc(GMEM_FIXED | GMEM_ZEROINIT, NFFLWoody[i].NumClasses*sizeof(WoodyData)))==NULL)
7242 // return false;
7243 if((NFFLWoody[11].wd=new WoodyData[NFFLWoody[i].NumClasses])==NULL)
7244 return false;
7245// ZeroMemory(NFFLWoody[11].wd, NFFLWoody[i].NumClasses*sizeof(WoodyData));
7246 memset(NFFLWoody[11].wd,0x0, NFFLWoody[i].NumClasses*sizeof(WoodyData));
7247 NFFLWoody[i].wd[0].SurfaceAreaToVolume=1500.0;
7248 NFFLWoody[i].wd[0].Load=4.01;
7249 NFFLWoody[i].wd[1].SurfaceAreaToVolume=109.0;
7250 NFFLWoody[i].wd[1].Load=14.03;
7251 NFFLWoody[i].wd[2].SurfaceAreaToVolume=30.0;
7252 NFFLWoody[i++].wd[2].Load=16.53;
7253 // fuel model 13
7254 NFFLWoody[i].NumClasses=3;
7255 NFFLWoody[i].Depth=3.0;
7256 NFFLWoody[i].Units=1;
7257 // if((NFFLWoody[12].wd=(WoodyData *) calloc(NFFLWoody[i].NumClasses, sizeof(WoodyData)))==NULL)
7258 // if((NFFLWoody[12].wd=(WoodyData *) GlobalAlloc(GMEM_FIXED | GMEM_ZEROINIT, NFFLWoody[i].NumClasses*sizeof(WoodyData)))==NULL)
7259 // return false;
7260 if((NFFLWoody[12].wd=new WoodyData[NFFLWoody[i].NumClasses])==NULL)
7261 return false;
7262// ZeroMemory(NFFLWoody[12].wd, NFFLWoody[i].NumClasses*sizeof(WoodyData));
7263 memset(NFFLWoody[12].wd,0x0, NFFLWoody[i].NumClasses*sizeof(WoodyData));
7264 NFFLWoody[i].wd[0].SurfaceAreaToVolume=1500.0;
7265 NFFLWoody[i].wd[0].Load=7.01;
7266 NFFLWoody[i].wd[1].SurfaceAreaToVolume=109.0;
7267 NFFLWoody[i].wd[1].Load=23.04;
7268 NFFLWoody[i].wd[2].SurfaceAreaToVolume=30.0;
7269 NFFLWoody[i].wd[2].Load=28.05;
7270 long j;
7271 // convert all to metric
7272 for(i=0; i<13; i++)
7273 { NFFLWoody[i].Depth/=3.280839895;
7274 for(j=0; j<NFFLWoody[i].NumClasses; j++)
7275 { NFFLWoody[i].wd[j].SurfaceAreaToVolume*=3.280839895;
7276 NFFLWoody[i].wd[j].Load*=0.224169061;
7277 NFFLWoody[i].wd[j].HeatContent=8000.0*2.32599;
7278 NFFLWoody[i].wd[j].Density=513.0;
7279 NFFLWoody[i].TotalWeight+=NFFLWoody[i].wd[j].Load;
7280 }
7281 }
7282 */
7283 return true;
7284}
7285
7286
7287double Get1000HrMoisture(long ModelNumber, bool Average)
7288{
7289 long i, Num;
7290 double AvgMx, sav1000;
7291
7292 Num=0;
7293 AvgMx=0.0;
7294 sav1000=4.0/0.0106; // 4 inch diameter
7295 for(i=0; i<coarsewoody[ModelNumber-1].NumClasses; i++)
7296 { if(coarsewoody[ModelNumber-1].wd[i].SurfaceAreaToVolume>sav1000)
7297 continue;
7298 AvgMx+=coarsewoody[ModelNumber-1].wd[i].FuelMoisture;
7299 Num++;
7300 if(!Average) // pick first one
7301 break;
7302 }
7303 if(Num>0)
7304 AvgMx/=(double) Num;
7305 else
7306 AvgMx=0.0;
7307
7308 return AvgMx;
7309}

7312double GetWoodyFuelMoisture(long ModelNumber, long SizeClass)
7313{
7314 if (ModelNumber > MAXNUM_COARSEWOODY_MODELS)
7315 return 0.0;
7316
7317 if (coarsewoody[ModelNumber - 1].NumClasses < SizeClass)
7318 return 0.0;
7319
7320 return coarsewoody[ModelNumber - 1].wd[SizeClass].FuelMoisture;
7321}

7331
7332
7333void GetWoodyData(long WoodyModelNumber, long SurfModelNumber,
7334 long* NumClasses, WoodyData* woody, double* depth, double* load)
7335{
7336 bool Combine = false;
7337
7338 *NumClasses = 0;
7339 *load = 0.0;
7340
7341
7342 switch (WoodyCombineOptions(GETVAL))
7343 {
7344 case CWD_COMBINE_NEVER:
7345 Combine = false; break;
7346 case CWD_COMBINE_ALWAYS:
7347 Combine = true; break;
7348 case CWD_COMBINE_ABSENT:
7349 if (WoodyModelNumber < 1)
7350 Combine = true;
7351 else if (coarsewoody[WoodyModelNumber - 1].wd == 0)
7352 Combine = true;
7353 else
7354 Combine = false;
7355 break;
7356 }
7357
7358 if (Combine)
7359 {
7360 // gather surface fuel model data
7361 if (SurfModelNumber > 0 && SurfModelNumber < 14) // alloc the max
7362 {
7363 *NumClasses = NFFLWoody[SurfModelNumber - 1].NumClasses;//tempwoody.NumClasses=
7364 *depth = NFFLWoody[SurfModelNumber - 1].Depth; //tempwoody.Depth=
7365 *load = NFFLWoody[SurfModelNumber - 1].TotalWeight;//tempwoody.TotalWeight=
7366 memcpy(woody, NFFLWoody[SurfModelNumber - 1].wd,
7367 NFFLWoody[SurfModelNumber - 1].NumClasses * sizeof(WoodyData));
7368 }
7369 else if (SurfModelNumber > 0)
7370 {
7371 //double t1, t10, t100, tLH, tLW, s1, sLH, sLW, hd, hl, d, xm;
7372 double s1, hd, hl;
7373 long i = 0, j;
7374 NewFuel nf;
7375 memset(&nf, 0x0, sizeof(NewFuel));
7376
7377 GetNewFuel(SurfModelNumber, &nf);
7378 *depth = nf.depth;
7379 *load = 0.0;
7380 if (nf.h1 > 0.0)
7381 {
7382 woody[i].Load = nf.h1;//*0.224169061;
7383 woody[i].SurfaceAreaToVolume = s1;//*3.280839895;
7384 woody[i++].HeatContent = hd;//*2.32599;
7385 }
7386 if (nf.h10 > 0.0)
7387 {
7388 woody[i].Load = nf.h10;
7389 woody[i].SurfaceAreaToVolume = 109.0;//*3.280839895;
7390 woody[i++].HeatContent = hd;//*2.32599;
7391 }
7392 if (nf.h100 > 0.0)
7393 {
7394 woody[i].Load = nf.h100;
7395 woody[i].SurfaceAreaToVolume = 30;//*3.280839895;
7396 woody[i++].HeatContent = hd;//*2.32599;
7397 }
7398 if (nf.lw > 0.0)
7399 {
7400 woody[i].Load = nf.lw;
7401 woody[i].SurfaceAreaToVolume = nf.savlw;//*3.280839895;
7402 woody[i++].HeatContent = hl;//*2.32599;
7403 }
7404 if (nf.lh > 0.0)
7405 {
7406 woody[i].Load = nf.lh;
7407 woody[i].SurfaceAreaToVolume = nf.savlh;//*3.280839895;
7408 woody[i++].HeatContent = hl;//*2.32599;
7409 }
7410 for (j = 0; j < i; j++)
7411 {
7412 woody[j].Density = 513.0;
7413 *load += woody[j].Load;
7414 }
7415 *NumClasses = tempwoody.NumClasses = i;
7416 }
7417 }
7418 // patch into coarsewoody model data if present
7419 if (WoodyModelNumber > 0)
7420 {
7421 if (coarsewoody[WoodyModelNumber - 1].wd)
7422 {
7423 memcpy(&woody[*NumClasses],
7424 coarsewoody[WoodyModelNumber - 1].wd,
7425 coarsewoody[WoodyModelNumber - 1].NumClasses * sizeof(WoodyData));
7426 *NumClasses += coarsewoody[WoodyModelNumber - 1].NumClasses;
7427 *depth = coarsewoody[WoodyModelNumber - 1].Depth;
7428 *load += coarsewoody[WoodyModelNumber - 1].TotalWeight;
7429 }
7430 }
7431}
7432
7433
7434void GetCurrentFuelMoistures(long fuelmod, long woodymod, double* mxin,
7435 double* mxout, long NumMx)
7436{
7437 bool Combine;
7438 long i, NumClasses = 0;
7439
7440// ZeroMemory(mxout, 20 * sizeof(double));
7441 memset(mxout,0x0, 20 * sizeof(double));
7442
7443 switch (WoodyCombineOptions(GETVAL))
7444 {
7445 case CWD_COMBINE_NEVER:
7446 Combine = false; break;
7447 case CWD_COMBINE_ALWAYS:
7448 Combine = true; break;
7449 case CWD_COMBINE_ABSENT:
7450 if (woodymod < 1)
7451 Combine = true;
7452 else if (coarsewoody[woodymod - 1].wd == 0)
7453 Combine = true;
7454 else
7455 Combine = false;
7456 break;
7457 }
7458
7459 if (Combine)
7460 {
7461 if (fuelmod < 14)
7462 {
7463 switch (fuelmod)
7464 {
7465 case 0:
7466 break;
7467 case 1:
7468 memcpy(mxout, mxin, 3 * sizeof(double));
7469 NumClasses = 3;
7470 break;
7471 case 2:
7472 memcpy(mxout, mxin, 3 * sizeof(double));
7473 mxout[3] = mxin[5];
7474 NumClasses = 4;
7475 break;
7476 case 3:
7477 memcpy(mxout, mxin, 3 * sizeof(double));
7478 NumClasses = 3;
7479 break;
7480 case 4:
7481 memcpy(mxout, mxin, 3 * sizeof(double));
7482 mxout[3] = mxin[5];
7483 NumClasses = 4;
7484 break;
7485 case 5:
7486 memcpy(mxout, mxin, 3 * sizeof(double));
7487 mxout[3] = mxin[5];
7488 NumClasses = 4;
7489 break;
7490 case 6:
7491 memcpy(mxout, mxin, 3 * sizeof(double));
7492 NumClasses = 3;
7493 break;
7494 case 7:
7495 memcpy(mxout, mxin, 4 * sizeof(double));
7496 NumClasses = 4;
7497 break;
7498 case 8:
7499 memcpy(mxout, mxin, 3 * sizeof(double));
7500 NumClasses = 3;
7501 break;
7502 case 9:
7503 memcpy(mxout, mxin, 3 * sizeof(double));
7504 NumClasses = 3;
7505 break;
7506 case 10:
7507 memcpy(mxout, mxin, 3 * sizeof(double));
7508 mxout[3] = mxin[5];
7509 NumClasses = 4;
7510 break;
7511 case 11:
7512 memcpy(mxout, mxin, 3 * sizeof(double));
7513 NumClasses = 3;
7514 break;
7515 case 12:
7516 memcpy(mxout, mxin, 3 * sizeof(double));
7517 NumClasses = 3;
7518 break;
7519 case 13:
7520 memcpy(mxout, mxin, 3 * sizeof(double));
7521 NumClasses = 3;
7522 break;
7523 }
7524 }
7525 else
7526 {
7527 //if(FuelMod.TL1[fuelmod-14]>0.0) // always have 1, 10, 100 hr fuels
7528 mxout[NumClasses++] = mxin[0];
7529 //if(FuelMod.TL10[fuelmod-14]>0.0)
7530 mxout[NumClasses++] = mxin[1];
7531 //if(FuelMod.TL100[fuelmod-14]>0.0)
7532 mxout[NumClasses++] = mxin[2];
7533 if (newfuels[fuelmod].lh > 0.0)//FuelMod.TLLiveH[fuelmod-14]>0.0)
7534 mxout[NumClasses++] = mxin[6];
7535 if (newfuels[fuelmod].lw > 0.0)//FuelMod.TLLiveW[fuelmod-14]>0.0)
7536 mxout[NumClasses++] = mxin[5];
7537 }
7538 }
7539 if (woodymod > 0)
7540 {
7541 for (i = 0; i < coarsewoody[woodymod - 1].NumClasses; i++)
7542 mxout[NumClasses + i] = coarsewoody[woodymod - 1].wd[i].FuelMoisture;
7543 memcpy(&mxout[NumClasses], mxin, 3 * sizeof(double));
7544 mxout[3] = mxin[5];
7545 }
7546}

7617
7618
7619void ResetNewFuels()
7620{
7621 memset(newfuels, 0x0, 256 * sizeof(NewFuel));
7622
7623 InitializeNewFuel();
7624
7625 long i;
7626 for (i = 0; i < 257; i++)
7627 {
7628 if (newfuels[i].number)
7629 newfuels[i].number *= -1; // indicate permanence
7630 }
7631
7632 HAVE_CUST_MODELS = false;
7633}
7634
7635
7636bool SetNewFuel(NewFuel* newfuel)
7637{
7638 long FuelNum;
7639
7640 if (newfuel == 0)
7641 return false;
7642
7643 FuelNum = newfuel->number;
7644 if (FuelNum > 256 || FuelNum < 0)
7645 return false;
7646
7647 newfuel->number = 0;
7648 if (newfuel->h1 > 0.0)
7649 newfuel->number = FuelNum;
7650 else if (newfuel->h10 > 0.0)
7651 newfuel->number = FuelNum;
7652 else if (newfuel->h100 > 0.0)
7653 newfuel->number = FuelNum;
7654 else if (newfuel->lh > 0.0)
7655 newfuel->number = FuelNum;
7656 else if (newfuel->lw > 0.0)
7657 newfuel->number = FuelNum;
7658
7659 memcpy(&newfuels[FuelNum], newfuel, sizeof(NewFuel));
7660
7661 return true;
7662}
7663
7664
7665bool GetNewFuel(long number, NewFuel* newfuel)
7666{
7667 if (number < 0)
7668 return false;
7669
7670 if (newfuels[number].number == 0)
7671 return false;
7672
7673 if (newfuel != 0)
7674 {
7675 memcpy(newfuel, &newfuels[number], sizeof(NewFuel));
7676 newfuel->number = labs(newfuel->number); // return absolute value of number
7677 }
7678
7679 return true;
7680}
7681
7682
7683bool IsNewFuelReserved(long number)
7684{
7685 if (number < 0)
7686 return false;
7687
7688 if (newfuels[number].number < 0)
7689 return true;
7690
7691 return false;
7692}
7693
7694
7695double GetFuelDepth(int Number)
7696{
7697 if (Number < 0)
7698 return 0.0;
7699
7700 if (newfuels[Number].number == 0)
7701 return 0.0;
7702
7703 return newfuels[Number].depth;
7704}

8632
8633void trim(char* totrim)
8634{
8635 for (int i = strlen(totrim) - 1; i > 0; i--)
8636 {
8637 switch (totrim[i])
8638 {
8639 case '\n':
8640 case '\r':
8641 case '\t':
8642 case ' ':
8643 totrim[i] = '\0';
8644 break;
8645 default:
8646 i = -1;
8647 }
8648 }
8649 bool found=false;
8650 while(!found)
8651 {
8652 int j = 0;
8653 switch (totrim[0])
8654 {
8655 case '\n':
8656 case '\t':
8657 case ' ':
8658 for (j = 0; j < (int)strlen(totrim) - 1; j++)
8659 totrim[j] = totrim[j + 1];
8660 totrim[j] = '\0';
8661 break;
8662 default:
8663 found=true;
8664 break;
8665 }
8666 }
8667}
